Theory AOT_NaturalNumbers

1(*<*)
2theory AOT_NaturalNumbers
3  imports AOT_PLM AOT_PossibleWorlds
4  abbrevs one-to-one = ‹⇩1⇩-⇩1›
5      and onto = ‹⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o›
6begin
7(*>*)
8
9section‹Natural Numbers›
10 
11AOT_define CorrelatesOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ _›)
12  "1-1-cor": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & G↓ &
13                                   ∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy)) &
14                                   ∀y ([G]y → ∃!x([F]x & [R]xy))›
15
16AOT_define MapsTo :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⟶ _›)
17  "fFG:1": ‹R |: F ⟶ G ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & G↓ & ∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy))›
18
19AOT_define MapsToOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ _›)
20  "fFG:2": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⟶ G & ∀x∀y∀z (([F]x & [F]y & [G]z) → ([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y))›
21
22AOT_define MapsOnto :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o _›)
23  "fFG:3": ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⟶ G & ∀y ([G]y → ∃x([F]x & [R]xy))›
24
25AOT_define MapsOneToOneOnto :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o _›)
26  "fFG:4": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
27
28AOT_theorem "eq-1-1": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G ≡ R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
29proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
30  AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G›
31  AOT_hence A: ‹∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy))› and B: ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃!x([F]x & [R]xy))›
32    using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "1-1-cor"] "&E" by blast+
33  AOT_have C: ‹R |: F ⟶ G›
34  proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:1"]; rule "&I")
35    AOT_show ‹R↓ & F↓ & G↓› using "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] "&I" by metis
36  next
37    AOT_show ‹∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy))› by (rule A)
38  qed
39  AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
40  proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:4"]; rule "&I")
41    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G›
42    proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:2"]; rule "&I")
43      AOT_show ‹R |: F ⟶ G› using C.
44    next
45      AOT_show ‹∀x∀y∀z ([F]x & [F]y & [G]z → ([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y))›
46      proof(rule GEN; rule GEN; rule GEN; rule "→I"; rule "→I")
47        fix x y z
48        AOT_assume 1: ‹[F]x & [F]y & [G]z›
49        moreover AOT_assume 2: ‹[R]xz & [R]yz›
50        ultimately AOT_have 3: ‹∃!x ([F]x & [R]xz)› using B "&E" "∀E" "→E" by fast
51        AOT_show ‹x = y›
52          by (rule "uni-most"[THEN "→E", OF 3, THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x],
53                            THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y], THEN "→E"])
54             (metis "&I" "&E" 1 2)
55      qed
56    qed
57  next
58    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
59    proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:3"]; rule "&I")
60      AOT_show ‹R |: F ⟶ G› using C.
61    next
62      AOT_show ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃x ([F]x & [R]xy))›
63      proof(rule GEN; rule "→I")
64        fix y
65        AOT_assume ‹[G]y›
66        AOT_hence ‹∃!x ([F]x & [R]xy)› using B[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
67        AOT_hence ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy & ∀β (([F]β & [R]βy) → β = x))›
68          using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
69        then AOT_obtain x where ‹[F]x & [R]xy› using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
70        AOT_thus ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy)› by (rule "∃I")
71      qed
72    qed
73  qed
74next
75  AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
76  AOT_hence ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G› and ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G› using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:4"] "&E" by blast+
77  AOT_hence C: ‹R |: F ⟶ G›
78    and D: ‹∀x∀y∀z ([F]x & [F]y & [G]z → ([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y))›
79    and E: ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃x ([F]x & [R]xy))›
80    using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:2"] "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:3"] "&E" by blast+
81  AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G›
82  proof(rule "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]; safe intro!: "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
83    AOT_show ‹∀x ([F]x → ∃!y ([G]y & [R]xy))›
84      using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:1", OF C] "&E" by blast
85  next
86    AOT_show ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃!x ([F]x & [R]xy))›
87    proof (rule "GEN"; rule "→I")
88      fix y
89      AOT_assume 0: ‹[G]y›
90      AOT_hence ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy)› using E "∀E" "→E" by fast
91      then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹[F]a & [R]ay› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
92      moreover AOT_have ‹∀z ([F]z & [R]zy → z = a)›
93      proof (rule GEN; rule "→I")
94        fix z
95        AOT_assume ‹[F]z & [R]zy›
96        AOT_thus ‹z = a›
97          using D[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z], THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=a],
98                  THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y], THEN "→E", THEN "→E"]
99                a_prop 0 "&E" "&I" by metis
100      qed
101      ultimately AOT_have ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy & ∀z ([F]z & [R]zy → z = x))›
102        using "&I" "∃I"(2) by fast
103      AOT_thus ‹∃!x ([F]x & [R]xy)›
104        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by fast
105    qed
106  qed
107qed
108
109
110AOT_register_rigid_restricted_type
111  Ordinary: ‹O!κ›
112proof
113  AOT_modally_strict {
114    AOT_show ‹∃x O!x›
115      by (meson "B◇" "T◇" "o-objects-exist:1" "vdash-properties:10")
116  }
117next
118  AOT_modally_strict {
119    AOT_show ‹O!κ → κ↓› for κ
120      by (simp add: "deduction-theorem" "russell-axiom[exe,1].ψ_denotes_asm")
121  }
122next
123  AOT_modally_strict {
124    AOT_show ‹□(O!α → □O!α)› for α
125      by (simp add: RN "oa-facts:1")
126  }
127qed
128
129AOT_register_variable_names
130  Ordinary: u v r t s
131
132AOT_theorem "equi:1": ‹∃!u φ{u} ≡ ∃u (φ{u} & ∀v (φ{v} → v =⇩E u))›
133proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
134  AOT_assume ‹∃!u φ{u}›
135  AOT_hence ‹∃!x (O!x & φ{x})›.
136  AOT_hence ‹∃x (O!x & φ{x} & ∀β (O!β & φ{β} → β = x))›
137    using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
138  then AOT_obtain x where x_prop: ‹O!x & φ{x} & ∀β (O!β & φ{β} → β = x)› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
139  {
140    fix β
141    AOT_assume beta_ord: ‹O!β›
142    moreover AOT_assume ‹φ{β}›
143    ultimately AOT_have ‹β = x› using x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=β]] "&I" "→E" by blast
144    AOT_hence ‹β =⇩E x›
145      using "ord-=E=:1"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)[OF beta_ord], THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"], THEN "≡E"(1)]
146      by blast
147  }
148  AOT_hence ‹(O!β → (φ{β} → β =⇩E x))› for β
149    using "→I" by blast
150  AOT_hence ‹∀β(O!β → (φ{β} → β =⇩E x))›
151    by (rule GEN)
152  AOT_hence ‹O!x & φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x))›
153    using x_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "&I" by blast
154  AOT_hence ‹O!x & (φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x)))›
155    using "&E" "&I" by meson
156  AOT_thus ‹∃u (φ{u} & ∀v (φ{v} → v =⇩E u))›
157    using "∃I" by fast
158next
159  AOT_assume ‹∃u (φ{u} & ∀v (φ{v} → v =⇩E u))›
160  AOT_hence ‹∃x (O!x & (φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x))))›
161    by blast
162  then AOT_obtain x where x_prop: ‹O!x & (φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x)))›
163    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
164  AOT_have ‹∀y ([O!]y & φ{y} → y = x)›
165  proof(rule GEN; rule "→I")
166    fix y
167    AOT_assume ‹O!y & φ{y}›
168    AOT_hence ‹y =⇩E x› using x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y]]
169      using "→E" "&E" by blast
170    AOT_thus ‹y = x›
171      using "ord-=E=:1"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(2)[OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]], THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"], THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
172  qed
173  AOT_hence ‹[O!]x & φ{x} & ∀y ([O!]y & φ{y} → y = x)› using x_prop "&E" "&I" by meson
174  AOT_hence ‹∃x ([O!]x & φ{x} & ∀y ([O!]y & φ{y} → y = x))› by (rule "∃I")
175  AOT_hence ‹∃!x (O!x & φ{x})›
176    by (rule "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
177  AOT_thus ‹∃!u φ{u}›.
178qed
179
180AOT_define CorrelatesEOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E _›)
181  "equi:2": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & G↓ &
182                               ∀u ([F]u → ∃!v([G]v & [R]uv)) &
183                               ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u([F]u & [R]uv))›
184
185AOT_define EquinumerousE :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (infixl "≈⇩E" 50)
186  "equi:3": ‹F ≈⇩E G ≡⇩d⇩f ∃R (R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G)›
187
188text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
189AOT_theorem eq_den_1: ‹Π↓› if ‹Π ≈⇩E Π'›
190proof -
191  AOT_have ‹∃R (R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π')›
192    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] that by blast
193  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π'› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
194  AOT_thus ‹Π↓›
195    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
196qed
197
198text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
199AOT_theorem eq_den_2: ‹Π'↓› if ‹Π ≈⇩E Π'›
200proof -
201  AOT_have ‹∃R (R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π')›
202    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] that by blast
203  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π'› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
204  AOT_thus ‹Π'↓›
205    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
206qed
207
208AOT_theorem "eq-part:1": ‹F ≈⇩E F›
209proof (safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "equi:3"] "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "equi:2"] "∃I"(1))
210  fix x
211  AOT_assume 1: ‹O!x›
212  AOT_assume 2: ‹[F]x›
213  AOT_show ‹∃!v ([F]v & x =⇩E v)›
214  proof(rule "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)]; rule "∃I"(2)[where β=x]; safe dest!: "&E"(2) intro!:  "&I" "→I" 1 2 Ordinary.GEN "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF 1])
215    AOT_show ‹v =⇩E x› if ‹x =⇩E v› for v
216      by (metis that "ord=Eequiv:2"[THEN "→E"])
217  qed
218next
219  fix y
220  AOT_assume 1: ‹O!y›
221  AOT_assume 2: ‹[F]y›
222  AOT_show ‹∃!u ([F]u & u =⇩E y)›
223    by(safe dest!: "&E"(2) intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=y]
224            "&I" "→I" 1 2 GEN "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF 1])
225qed(auto simp: "=E[denotes]")
226
227
228AOT_theorem "eq-part:2": ‹F ≈⇩E G → G ≈⇩E F›
229proof (rule "→I")
230  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G›
231  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G› using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
232  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
233  AOT_hence 0: ‹R↓ & F↓ & G↓ & ∀u ([F]u → ∃!v([G]v & [R]uv)) &
234                            ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u([F]u & [R]uv))› using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
235
236  AOT_have ‹[λxy [R]yx]↓ & G↓ & F↓ & ∀u ([G]u → ∃!v([F]v & [λxy [R]yx]uv)) &
237                            ∀v ([F]v → ∃!u([G]u & [λxy [R]yx]uv))›
238  proof (AOT_subst ‹[λxy [R]yx]yx› ‹[R]xy› bound: x y;
239         (safe intro!: "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] 0[THEN "&E"(2)] 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]; "cqt:2[lambda]")?)
240    AOT_modally_strict {
241      AOT_have ‹[λxy [R]yx]xy› if ‹[R]yx› for y x
242        by(auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3" that)
243      moreover AOT_have ‹[R]yx› if ‹[λxy [R]yx]xy› for y x
244        using "β→C"(1)[where φ="λ(x,y). _ (x,y)" and κ⇩1κ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified, OF that, simplified].
245      ultimately AOT_show ‹[λxy [R]yx]αβ ≡ [R]βα› for α β
246        by (metis "deduction-theorem" "≡I")
247    }
248  qed
249  AOT_hence ‹[λxy [R]yx] |: G ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E F› using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by blast
250  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: G ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E F› by (rule "∃I"(1)) "cqt:2[lambda]"
251  AOT_thus ‹G ≈⇩E F›
252    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by blast
253qed
254
255text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
256AOT_theorem "eq-part:2[terms]": ‹Π ≈⇩E Π' → Π' ≈⇩E Π›
257  using "eq-part:2"[unvarify F G] eq_den_1 eq_den_2 "→I" by meson
258declare "eq-part:2[terms]"[THEN "→E", sym]
259
260AOT_theorem "eq-part:3": ‹(F ≈⇩E G & G ≈⇩E H) → F ≈⇩E H›
261proof (rule "→I")
262  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G & G ≈⇩E H›
263  then AOT_obtain R⇩1 and R⇩2 where
264       ‹R⇩1 |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
265   and ‹R⇩2 |: G ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H›
266    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by metis
267  AOT_hence θ: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v([G]v & [R⇩1]uv)) & ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u([F]u & [R⇩1]uv))›
268        and ξ: ‹∀u ([G]u → ∃!v([H]v & [R⇩2]uv)) & ∀v ([H]v → ∃!u([G]u & [R⇩2]uv))›
269    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)]
270          "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]
271          "&I" by blast+
272  AOT_have ‹∃R R = [λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]›
273    by (rule "free-thms:3[lambda]") cqt_2_lambda_inst_prover
274  then AOT_obtain R where R_def: ‹R = [λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]›
275    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
276  AOT_have 1: ‹∃!v (([H]v & [R]uv))› if a: ‹[O!]u› and b: ‹[F]u› for u
277  proof (rule "≡E"(2)[OF "equi:1"])
278    AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹[O!]b & ([G]b & [R⇩1]ub & ∀v ([G]v & [R⇩1]uv → v =⇩E b))›
279      using θ[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF a b, THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
280            "∃E"[rotated] by blast
281    AOT_obtain c where c_prop: "[O!]c & ([H]c & [R⇩2]bc & ∀v ([H]v & [R⇩2]bv → v =⇩E c))"
282      using ξ[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=b], THEN "→E", OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "→E",
283          OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
284    "∃E"[rotated] by blast
285    AOT_show ‹∃v ([H]v & [R]uv & ∀v' ([H]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
286    proof (safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "∃I"(2)[where β=c])
287      AOT_show ‹O!c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
288    next
289      AOT_show ‹[H]c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
290    next
291      AOT_have 0: ‹[O!]u & [O!]c & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]uv & [R⇩2]vc)›
292        by (safe intro!: "&I" a c_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "∃I"(2)[where β=b] b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
293                     b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1)] c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
294      AOT_show ‹[R]uc›
295        by (auto intro: "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def[symmetric]]
296                 intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3" 0)
297    next
298      fix x
299      AOT_assume ordx: ‹O!x›
300      AOT_assume ‹[H]x & [R]ux›
301      AOT_hence hx: ‹[H]x› and ‹[R]ux› using "&E" by blast+
302      AOT_hence ‹[λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]ux›
303        using "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def] by fast
304      AOT_hence ‹O!u & O!x & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]uv & [R⇩2]vx)›
305        by (rule "β→C"(1)[where φ="λ(κ,κ'). _ κ κ'" and κ⇩1κ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
306      then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹O!z & ([G]z & [R⇩1]uz & [R⇩2]zx)›
307        using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
308      AOT_hence ‹z =⇩E b› using b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z]]
309        using "&E" "→E" by metis
310      AOT_hence ‹z = b› by (metis "=E-simple:2"[THEN "→E"])
311      AOT_hence ‹[R⇩2]bx› using z_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2)] "rule=E" by fast
312      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩E c›
313        using c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x], THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF ordx]
314              hx "&I" by blast
315    qed
316  qed
317  AOT_have 2: ‹∃!u (([F]u & [R]uv))› if a: ‹[O!]v› and b: ‹[H]v› for v
318  proof (rule "≡E"(2)[OF "equi:1"])
319    AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹[O!]b & ([G]b & [R⇩2]bv & ∀u ([G]u & [R⇩2]uv → u =⇩E b))›
320      using ξ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF a b, THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
321            "∃E"[rotated] by blast
322    AOT_obtain c where c_prop: "[O!]c & ([F]c & [R⇩1]cb & ∀v ([F]v & [R⇩1]vb → v =⇩E c))"
323      using θ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=b], THEN "→E", OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "→E",
324          OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
325    "∃E"[rotated] by blast
326    AOT_show ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uv & ∀v' ([F]v' & [R]v'v → v' =⇩E u))›
327    proof (safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "∃I"(2)[where β=c])
328      AOT_show ‹O!c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
329    next
330      AOT_show ‹[F]c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
331    next
332      AOT_have ‹[O!]c & [O!]v & ∃u ([G]u & [R⇩1]cu & [R⇩2]uv)›
333        by (safe intro!: "&I" a c_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "∃I"(2)[where β=b] b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
334                     b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
335                     b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]
336                     c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
337      AOT_thus ‹[R]cv›
338        by (auto intro: "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def[symmetric]] intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2"
339                 simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
340    next
341      fix x
342      AOT_assume ordx: ‹O!x›
343      AOT_assume ‹[F]x & [R]xv›
344      AOT_hence hx: ‹[F]x› and ‹[R]xv› using "&E" by blast+
345      AOT_hence ‹[λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]xv›
346        using "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def] by fast
347      AOT_hence ‹O!x & O!v & ∃u ([G]u & [R⇩1]xu & [R⇩2]uv)›
348        by (rule "β→C"(1)[where φ="λ(κ,κ'). _ κ κ'" and κ⇩1κ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
349      then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹O!z & ([G]z & [R⇩1]xz & [R⇩2]zv)›
350        using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
351      AOT_hence ‹z =⇩E b› using b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z]]
352        using "&E" "→E" "&I" by metis
353      AOT_hence ‹z = b› by (metis "=E-simple:2"[THEN "→E"])
354      AOT_hence ‹[R⇩1]xb› using z_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] "rule=E" by fast
355      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩E c›
356        using c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x], THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF ordx]
357              hx "&I" by blast
358    qed
359  qed
360  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E H›
361    apply (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
362    apply (rule "∃I"(2)[where β=R])
363    by (auto intro!: 1 2 "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I" Ordinary.ψ)
364qed

366text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
367AOT_theorem "eq-part:3[terms]": ‹Π ≈⇩E Π''› if ‹Π ≈⇩E Π'› and ‹Π' ≈⇩E Π''›
368  using "eq-part:3"[unvarify F G H, THEN "→E"] eq_den_1 eq_den_2 "→I" "&I"
369  by (metis that(1) that(2))
370declare "eq-part:3[terms]"[trans]
371
372AOT_theorem "eq-part:4": ‹F ≈⇩E G ≡ ∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
373proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
374  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
375  AOT_hence 1: ‹G ≈⇩E F› using "eq-part:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
376  AOT_show ‹∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
377  proof (rule GEN; rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
378    AOT_show ‹H ≈⇩E G› if ‹H ≈⇩E F› for H using 0
379      by (meson "&I" "eq-part:3" that "vdash-properties:6")
380  next
381    AOT_show ‹H ≈⇩E F› if ‹H ≈⇩E G› for H using 1
382      by (metis "&I" "eq-part:3" that "vdash-properties:6")
383  qed
384next
385  AOT_assume ‹∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
386  AOT_hence ‹F ≈⇩E F ≡ F ≈⇩E G› using "∀E" by blast
387  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E G› using "eq-part:1" "≡E" by blast
388qed

394  "equi-rem:2": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⟶E G & ∀t∀u∀v (([F]t & [F]u & [G]v) → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›

400  "equi-rem:4": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›

402AOT_theorem "equi-rem-thm": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G ≡ R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
403proof -
404  AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G ≡ R |: [λx O!x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx O!x & [G]x]›
405  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "&I")
406    AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
407    AOT_hence ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))› and ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
408      using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
409    AOT_hence a: ‹([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))› and b: ‹([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))› for u v
410      using "Ordinary.∀E" by fast+
411    AOT_have ‹([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))› for x
412      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x› ‹[O!]x & [F]x›)
413       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
414       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
415      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]x› ‹[O!]x & [G]x› bound: x)
416       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
417       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
418      apply (AOT_subst ‹O!y & [G]y & [R]xy› ‹O!y & ([G]y & [R]xy)› bound: y)
419       apply (meson "≡E"(6) "Associativity of &" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
420      apply (rule "→I") apply (frule "&E"(1)) apply (drule "&E"(2))
421      by (fact a[unconstrain u, THEN "→E", THEN "→E", of x])
422    AOT_hence A: ‹∀x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))› by (rule GEN)
423    AOT_have ‹([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))› for y
424      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]y› ‹[O!]y & [G]y›)
425       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
426       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
427      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x› ‹[O!]x & [F]x› bound: x)
428       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
429       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
430      apply (AOT_subst ‹O!x & [F]x & [R]xy› ‹O!x & ([F]x & [R]xy)› bound: x)
431       apply (meson "≡E"(6) "Associativity of &" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
432      apply (rule "→I") apply (frule "&E"(1)) apply (drule "&E"(2))
433      by (fact b[unconstrain v, THEN "→E", THEN "→E", of y])
434    AOT_hence B: ‹∀y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))› by (rule GEN)
435    AOT_show ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
436      by (safe intro!: "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] A B)
437          "cqt:2[lambda]"+
438  next
439    AOT_assume ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
440    AOT_hence a: ‹([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))› and 
441              b: ‹([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))› for x y
442      using "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" "∀E"(2) by blast+
443    AOT_have ‹[F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)› for u
444    proof (safe intro!: "→I")
445      AOT_assume fu: ‹[F]u›
446      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]u›
447        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.ψ fu "&I")
448      AOT_show ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)›
449        apply (AOT_subst ‹[O!]x & ([G]x & [R]ux)› ‹([O!]x & [G]x) & [R]ux› bound: x)
450         apply (simp add: "Associativity of &")
451        apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[O!]x & [G]x› ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]x› bound: x)
452         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
453         apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
454        using a[THEN "→E", OF 0] by blast
455    qed
456    AOT_hence A: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
457    AOT_have ‹[G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv)› for v
458    proof (safe intro!: "→I")
459      AOT_assume gu: ‹[G]v›
460      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]v›
461        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.ψ gu "&I")
462      AOT_show ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv)›
463        apply (AOT_subst ‹[O!]x & ([F]x & [R]xv)› ‹([O!]x & [F]x) & [R]xv› bound: x)
464         apply (simp add: "Associativity of &")
465        apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[O!]x & [F]x›‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x›  bound: x)
466         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
467         apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
468        using b[THEN "→E", OF 0] by blast
469    qed
470    AOT_hence B: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
471    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
472      by (safe intro!: "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" A B "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
473  qed
474  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
475  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "&I")
476    AOT_assume ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
477    AOT_hence a: ‹([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))› and 
478              b: ‹([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))› for x y
479      using "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" "∀E"(2) by blast+
480    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
481    proof (safe intro!: "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "equi-rem:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
482                        "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "equi-rem:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
483                        "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I")
484      fix u
485      AOT_assume fu: ‹[F]u›
486      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]u›
487        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.ψ fu "&I")
488      AOT_hence 1: ‹∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]uy)› using a[THEN "→E"] by blast
489      AOT_show ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)›
490        apply (AOT_subst ‹[O!]x & ([G]x & [R]ux)› ‹([O!]x & [G]x) & [R]ux› bound: x)
491         apply (simp add: "Associativity of &")
492        apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[O!]x & [G]x› ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]x› bound: x)
493         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
494         apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
495        by (fact 1)
496    next
497      fix t u v
498      AOT_assume ‹[F]t & [F]u & [G]v› and rtv_tuv: ‹[R]tv & [R]uv›
499      AOT_hence oft: ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]t› and
500                ofu: ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]u› and
501                ogv: ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]v›
502        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I"
503                 simp: Ordinary.ψ dest: "&E")
504      AOT_hence ‹∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xv)›
505        using b[THEN "→E"] by blast
506      then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]a & [R]av & ∀x (([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xv) → x = a)›
507        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
508      AOT_hence ua: ‹u = a› using ofu rtv_tuv[THEN "&E"(2)] "∀E"(2) "→E" "&I" "&E"(2) by blast
509      moreover AOT_have ta: ‹t = a› using a_prop oft rtv_tuv[THEN "&E"(1)] "∀E"(2) "→E" "&I" "&E"(2) by blast
510      ultimately AOT_have ‹t = u› by (metis "rule=E" id_sym)
511      AOT_thus ‹t =⇩E u› using "rule=E" id_sym "ord=Eequiv:1" Ordinary.ψ ta ua "vdash-properties:10" by fast
512    next
513      fix u
514      AOT_assume ‹[F]u›
515      AOT_hence ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]u›
516        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I"
517                 simp: "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]  Ordinary.ψ)
518      AOT_hence ‹∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]uy)›
519        using a[THEN "→E"] by blast
520      then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]a & [R]ua & ∀x (([λx [O!]x & [G]x]x & [R]ux) → x = a)›
521        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
522      AOT_have ‹O!a & [G]a›
523        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)])
524      AOT_hence ‹O!a› and ‹[G]a› using "&E" by blast+
525      moreover AOT_have ‹∀v ([G]v & [R]uv → v =⇩E a)›
526      proof(safe intro!: Ordinary.GEN "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
527        fix v
528        AOT_assume ‹[G]v› and ruv: ‹[R]uv›
529        AOT_hence ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]v›
530          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" simp: Ordinary.ψ)
531        AOT_hence ‹v = a› using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", OF "&I"] ruv by blast
532        AOT_thus ‹v =⇩E a› using "rule=E" "ord=Eequiv:1" Ordinary.ψ "vdash-properties:10" by fast
533      qed
534      ultimately AOT_have ‹O!a & ([G]a & [R]ua & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E a))›
535        using "∃I" "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] by simp
536      AOT_hence ‹∃v ([G]v & [R]uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E v))› by (rule "∃I")
537      AOT_thus ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)›
538        by (rule "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
539    next
540      fix v
541      AOT_assume ‹[G]v›
542      AOT_hence ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]v›
543        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" Ordinary.ψ)
544      AOT_hence ‹∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xv)› using b[THEN "→E"] by blast
545      then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]a & [R]av & ∀y ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]y & [R]yv → y = a)›
546        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "∃E"[rotated]] by blast
547      AOT_have ‹O!a & [F]a›
548        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)])
549      AOT_hence ‹O!a & ([F]a & [R]av)› using a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] "&E" "&I" by metis
550      AOT_thus ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uv)› by (rule "∃I")
551    qed
552  next
553    AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
554    AOT_hence 1: ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G› and 2: ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G› using "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
555    AOT_hence 3: ‹R |: F ⟶E G› and A: ‹∀t ∀u ∀v ([F]t & [F]u & [G]v → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›
556      using "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF 1] "&E" by blast+
557    AOT_hence B: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))› using "equi-rem:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
558    AOT_have C: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃u ([F]u & [R]uv))› using "equi-rem:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF 2] "&E" by blast
559    AOT_show ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
560    proof (rule "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]; safe intro!: "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] GEN "→I")
561      AOT_show ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
562    next
563      AOT_show ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
564    next
565      fix x
566      AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x›
567      AOT_have ‹O!x & [F]x›
568        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1)
569      AOT_hence ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]xv)›
570        using B[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast
571      then AOT_obtain y where y_prop: ‹O!y & ([G]y & [R]xy & ∀u ([G]u & [R]xu → u =⇩E y))›
572        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "∃E"[rotated] by fastforce
573      AOT_hence ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]y›
574        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" dest: "&E")
575      moreover AOT_have ‹∀z ([λx O!x & [G]x]z & [R]xz → z = y)›
576      proof(safe intro!: GEN "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
577        fix z
578        AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]z›
579        AOT_have 2: ‹O!z & [G]z›
580          by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1)
581        moreover AOT_assume ‹[R]xz›
582        ultimately AOT_have ‹z =⇩E y›
583          using y_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E", rotated, OF "&I"] "&E"
584          by blast
585        AOT_thus ‹z = y› using 2[THEN "&E"(1)] by (metis "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:10")
586      qed
587      ultimately AOT_have ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]y & [R]xy & ∀z ([λx O!x & [G]x]z & [R]xz → z = y)›
588        using y_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] "&I" by auto
589      AOT_hence ‹∃y ([λx O!x & [G]x]y & [R]xy & ∀z ([λx O!x & [G]x]z & [R]xz → z = y))›
590        by (rule "∃I")
591      AOT_thus ‹∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy)›
592        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by fast
593    next
594      fix y
595      AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]y›
596      AOT_have oy_gy: ‹O!y & [G]y›
597        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1)
598      AOT_hence ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uy)›
599        using C[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast
600      then AOT_obtain x where x_prop: ‹O!x & ([F]x & [R]xy)›
601        using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
602      AOT_hence ofx: ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]x›
603        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" dest: "&E")
604      AOT_have ‹∃α ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]α & [R]αy & ∀β ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]β & [R]βy → β = α))›
605      proof (safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=x] "&I" GEN "→I")
606        AOT_show ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]x› using ofx.
607      next
608        AOT_show ‹[R]xy› using x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2)].
609      next
610        fix z
611        AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]z & [R]zy›
612        AOT_have oz_fz: ‹O!z & [F]z›
613          by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1[THEN "&E"(1)])
614        AOT_have ‹z =⇩E x›
615          using A[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z], THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x], THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y], THEN "→E",
616                THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF oz_fz[THEN "&E"(1)], OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], OF oy_gy[THEN "&E"(1)], OF "&I", OF "&I",
617                OF oz_fz[THEN "&E"(2)], OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1)], OF oy_gy[THEN "&E"(2)], OF "&I",
618                OF 1[THEN "&E"(2)], OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2)]].
619        AOT_thus ‹z = x›
620          by (metis "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:10")
621      qed
622      AOT_thus ‹∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy)›
623        by (rule "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
624    qed
625  qed
626  finally show ?thesis.
627qed
628
629AOT_theorem "empty-approx:1": ‹(¬∃u [F]u & ¬∃v [H]v) → F ≈⇩E H›
630proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
631  AOT_assume 0: ‹¬∃u [F]u› and 1: ‹¬∃v [H]v›
632  AOT_have ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([H]v & [R]uv))› for R
633  proof(rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "→I"; rule "raa-cor:1")
634    fix u
635    AOT_assume ‹[F]u›
636    AOT_hence ‹∃u [F]u› using "Ordinary.∃I" "&I" by fast
637    AOT_thus ‹∃u [F]u & ¬∃u [F]u› using "&I" 0 by blast
638  qed
639  moreover AOT_have ‹∀v ([H]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))› for R
640  proof(rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "→I"; rule "raa-cor:1")
641    fix v
642    AOT_assume ‹[H]v›
643    AOT_hence ‹∃v [H]v› using "Ordinary.∃I" "&I" by fast
644    AOT_thus ‹∃v [H]v & ¬∃v [H]v› using 1 "&I" by blast
645  qed
646  ultimately AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H› for R
647    apply (safe intro!: "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" GEN "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
648    using "∀E" by blast+
649  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H› by (rule "∃I")
650  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E H›
651    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
652qed
653
654AOT_theorem "empty-approx:2": ‹(∃u [F]u & ¬∃v [H]v) → ¬(F ≈⇩E H)›
655proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2); rule "raa-cor:2")
656  AOT_assume 1: ‹∃u [F]u› and 2: ‹¬∃v [H]v›
657  AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹O!b & [F]b› using 1 "∃E"[rotated] by blast
658  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E H›
659  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H›
660    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"])
661  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
662  AOT_hence θ: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([H]v & [R]uv))› and ‹∀v ([H]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
663    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
664  AOT_have ‹∃!v ([H]v & [R]bv)› for u
665    using θ[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=b], THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]].
666  AOT_hence ‹∃v ([H]v & [R]bv & ∀u ([H]u & [R]bu → u =⇩E v))›
667    by (rule "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)])
668  then AOT_obtain x where ‹O!x & ([H]x & [R]bx & ∀u ([H]u & [R]bu → u =⇩E x))› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
669  AOT_hence ‹O!x & [H]x› using "&E" "&I" by blast
670  AOT_hence ‹∃v [H]v› by (rule "∃I")
671  AOT_thus ‹∃v [H]v & ¬∃v [H]v› using 2 "&I" by blast
672qed

675AOT_define FminusU :: ‹Π ⇒ τ ⇒ Π› ("_⇧-⇧_")
676  "F-u": ‹[F]⇧-⇧x =⇩d⇩f [λz [F]z & z ≠⇩E x]›
677
678text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
679AOT_theorem "F-u[den]": ‹[F]⇧-⇧x↓›
680  by (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "F-u", where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
681
682AOT_theorem eqP': ‹F ≈⇩E G & [F]u & [G]v → [F]⇧-⇧u ≈⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
683proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(2); drule "&E"(1); frule "&E"(2); drule "&E"(1))
684  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G›
685  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
686    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
687  then AOT_obtain R where R_prop: ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
688  AOT_hence A: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))› and B: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
689    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
690  AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G› using "equi-rem-thm"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF R_prop].
691  AOT_hence ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G› using "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
692  AOT_hence C: ‹∀t∀u∀v (([F]t & [F]u & [G]v) → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›
693    using "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
694  AOT_assume fu: ‹[F]u›
695  AOT_assume gv: ‹[G]v›
696  AOT_have ‹[λz [Π]z & z ≠⇩E κ]↓› for Π κ by "cqt:2[lambda]"
697  note Π_minus_κI = "rule-id-df:2:b[2]"[where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]
698   and Π_minus_κE = "rule-id-df:2:a[2]"[where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]
699  AOT_have Π_minus_κ_den: ‹[Π]⇧-⇧κ↓› for Π κ (* TODO: PLM: quietly dismissed *)
700    by (rule Π_minus_κI) "cqt:2[lambda]"+
701  {
702    fix R
703    AOT_assume R_prop: ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
704    AOT_hence A: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))› and B: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
705      using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
706    AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G› using "equi-rem-thm"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF R_prop].
707    AOT_hence ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G› using "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
708    AOT_hence C: ‹∀t∀u∀v (([F]t & [F]u & [G]v) → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›
709      using "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
710
711    AOT_assume Ruv: ‹[R]uv›
712    AOT_have ‹R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
713    proof(safe intro!: "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Π_minus_κ_den Ordinary.GEN "→I")
714      fix u'
715      AOT_assume ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]u'›
716      AOT_hence 0: ‹[λz [F]z & z ≠⇩E u]u'› using Π_minus_κE by fast
717      AOT_have 0: ‹[F]u' & u' ≠⇩E u›
718        by (rule "β→C"(1)[where κ⇩1κ⇩n="AOT_term_of_var (Ordinary.Rep u')"]) (fact 0)
719      AOT_have ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]u'v)›
720        using A[THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=u'], THEN "→E", OF 0[THEN "&E"(1)]].
721      then AOT_obtain v' where v'_prop: ‹[G]v' & [R]u'v' & ∀ t ([G]t & [R]u't → t =⇩E v')›
722        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by fastforce
723
724      AOT_show ‹∃!v' ([[G]⇧-⇧v]v' & [R]u'v')›
725      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=v'] "&I" Ordinary.GEN "→I")
726        AOT_show ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]v'›
727        proof (rule Π_minus_κI; 
728               safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "thm-neg=E"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
729          AOT_show ‹[G]v'› using v'_prop "&E" by blast
730        next
731          AOT_show ‹¬v' =⇩E v›
732          proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
733            AOT_assume ‹v' =⇩E v›
734            AOT_hence ‹v' = v› by (metis "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:10")
735            AOT_hence Ruv': ‹[R]uv'› using "rule=E" Ruv id_sym by fast
736            AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E u›
737              by (rule C[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=v'], THEN "→E", THEN "→E"])
738                 (safe intro!: "&I" 0[THEN "&E"(1)] fu v'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
739                                Ruv' v'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
740            moreover AOT_have ‹¬(u' =⇩E u)›
741              using "0" "&E"(2) "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E" by blast
742            ultimately AOT_show ‹u' =⇩E u & ¬u' =⇩E u› using "&I" by blast
743          qed
744        qed
745      next
746        AOT_show ‹[R]u'v'› using v'_prop "&E" by blast
747      next
748        fix t
749        AOT_assume t_prop: ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]t & [R]u't›
750        AOT_have gt_t_noteq_v: ‹[G]t & t ≠⇩E v›
751          apply (rule "β→C"(1)[where κ⇩1κ⇩n="AOT_term_of_var (Ordinary.Rep t)"])
752          apply (rule Π_minus_κE)
753          by (fact t_prop[THEN "&E"(1)])
754        AOT_show ‹t =⇩E v'›
755          using v'_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E",
756                        OF "&I", OF gt_t_noteq_v[THEN "&E"(1)], OF t_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]].
757      qed
758    next
759      fix v'
760      AOT_assume G_minus_v_v': ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]v'›
761      AOT_have gt_t_noteq_v: ‹[G]v' & v' ≠⇩E v›
762        apply (rule "β→C"(1)[where κ⇩1κ⇩n="AOT_term_of_var (Ordinary.Rep v')"])
763        apply (rule Π_minus_κE)
764        by (fact G_minus_v_v')
765      AOT_have ‹∃!u([F]u & [R]uv')› using B[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E", OF gt_t_noteq_v[THEN "&E"(1)]].
766      then AOT_obtain u' where u'_prop: ‹[F]u' & [R]u'v' & ∀t ([F]t & [R]tv' → t =⇩E u')›
767        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by fastforce
768      AOT_show ‹∃!u' ([[F]⇧-⇧u]u' & [R]u'v')›
769      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u'] "&I" Ordinary.GEN "→I" u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
770        AOT_show ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]u'›
771        proof (rule Π_minus_κI;
772               safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "thm-neg=E"[THEN "≡E"(2)]
773               u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]; rule "raa-cor:2")
774          AOT_assume u'_eq_u: ‹u' =⇩E u›
775          AOT_hence ‹u' = u›
776            using "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
777          AOT_hence Ru'v: ‹[R]u'v› using "rule=E" Ruv id_sym by fast
778          AOT_have ‹v' ≠⇩E v›
779            using "&E"(2) gt_t_noteq_v by blast
780          AOT_hence v'_noteq_v: ‹¬(v' =⇩E v)› by (metis "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E")
781          AOT_have ‹∃u ([G]u & [R]u'u & ∀v ([G]v & [R]u'v → v =⇩E u))›
782            using A[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E", OF u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)],
783                    THEN "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)]].
784          then AOT_obtain t where t_prop: ‹[G]t & [R]u't & ∀v ([G]v & [R]u'v → v =⇩E t)›
785            using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
786          AOT_have ‹v =⇩E t› if ‹[G]v› and ‹[R]u'v› for v
787            using t_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF that].
788          AOT_hence ‹v' =⇩E t› and ‹v =⇩E t›
789            by (auto simp:  gt_t_noteq_v[THEN "&E"(1)] u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] Ru'v gv)
790          AOT_hence ‹v' =⇩E v› using "rule=E" "=E-simple:2" id_sym "vdash-properties:10" by fast
791          AOT_thus ‹v' =⇩E v & ¬v' =⇩E v› using v'_noteq_v "&I" by blast
792        qed
793      next
794        fix t
795        AOT_assume 0: ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]t & [R]tv'›
796        moreover AOT_have ‹[F]t & t ≠⇩E u›
797          apply (rule "β→C"(1)[where κ⇩1κ⇩n="AOT_term_of_var (Ordinary.Rep t)"])
798          apply (rule Π_minus_κE)

1052            by (metis "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "∨E"(3) not_v_eq_b "raa-cor:3")
1053          AOT_hence ‹(u' =⇩E u & v =⇩E v)› using 2 by (metis "∨E"(2))
1054          AOT_thus ‹u' =⇩E u› using "&E" by blast
1055        qed
1056      }
1057      moreover {
1058        AOT_assume 0: ‹v' =⇩E b›
1059        AOT_hence v'_eq_b: ‹v' = b›
1060          using "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
1061        AOT_have ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R⇩1]uv')›
1062        proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=a] "&I" Ordinary.GEN "→I" b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
1063                            b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)] oa fa)
1064          AOT_show ‹[R⇩1]av'›
1065            apply (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF R⇩1_def[symmetric]])
1066            apply (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" prod_denotesI)
1067            apply (rule "∨I"(1); rule "∨I"(2); rule "&I")
1068            using oa "ord=Eequiv:1" "vdash-properties:10" apply blast
1069            using "0" by blast
1070        next
1071          fix u'
1072          AOT_assume fu'_R1u'v': ‹[F]u' & [R⇩1]u'v'›
1073          AOT_hence 0: ‹[R⇩1]u'b› using v'_eq_b by (meson "rule=E" "&E"(2))
1074          AOT_have 1: ‹[«?R»]u'b›
1075            by (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF R⇩1_def]) (fact 0)
1076          AOT_have ‹(u' ≠⇩E u & b ≠⇩E v & [R]u'b) ∨ (u' =⇩E a & b =⇩E b) ∨ (u' =⇩E u & b =⇩E v)›
1077            using "β→C"(1)[OF 1, simplified] by simp
1078          moreover {
1079            AOT_assume 0: ‹u' ≠⇩E u & b ≠⇩E v & [R]u'b›
1080            AOT_have ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv')› using B[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E", OF gv'].
1081            AOT_hence ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]ub)› using v'_eq_b "rule=E" by fast
1082            AOT_hence ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]ub & ∀t ([F]t & [R]tb → t =⇩E u))›
1083              using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by fast
1084            then AOT_obtain s where s_prop: ‹[F]s & [R]sb & ∀t ([F]t & [R]tb → t =⇩E s)› using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
1085            AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E s› using s_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"]
1086                                     fu'_R1u'v'[THEN "&E"(1)] 0[THEN "&E"(2)]
1087              by (metis "&I" "vdash-properties:10")
1088            moreover AOT_have ‹u =⇩E s› using s_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"]
1089                                    fu Rub by (metis "&I" "vdash-properties:10")
1090            ultimately AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E u›
1091              by (metis "&I" "ord=Eequiv:2" "ord=Eequiv:3" "vdash-properties:10")
1092            moreover AOT_have ‹¬(u' =⇩E u)› using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)] by (metis "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E") 
1093            ultimately AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E a› by (metis "raa-cor:3")
1094          }
1095          moreover {
1096            AOT_assume ‹u' =⇩E u & b =⇩E v›
1097            AOT_hence ‹u' =⇩E a› by (metis "&E"(2) not_b_eq_v "reductio-aa:1")
1098          }
1099          ultimately AOT_show ‹u' =⇩E a› by (metis "&E"(1) "∨E"(3) "reductio-aa:1") 
1100        qed
1101      }
1102      ultimately AOT_show ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R⇩1]uv')› by (metis "raa-cor:1")
1103    qed
1104    ultimately AOT_have ‹∃R R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v› using 1 by blast
1105  }
1106  ultimately AOT_have ‹∃R R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v› using R_prop by (metis "reductio-aa:2") 
1107  AOT_thus ‹[F]⇧-⇧u ≈⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
1108    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
1109qed

1112AOT_theorem "P'-eq": ‹[F]⇧-⇧u ≈⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v & [F]u & [G]v → F ≈⇩E G›
1113proof(safe intro!: "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2); frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))

1115  note Π_minus_κI = "rule-id-df:2:b[2]"[where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]
1116   and Π_minus_κE = "rule-id-df:2:a[2]"[where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]

1131  qed

1138  then AOT_obtain R where R_prop: ‹R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1139  AOT_hence Fact1: ‹∀r([[F]⇧-⇧u]r → ∃!s ([[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]rs))› and Fact1': ‹∀s([[G]⇧-⇧v]s → ∃!r ([[F]⇧-⇧u]r & [R]rs))›
1140    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+

1264      using "≡E"(2) "equi:1" "reductio-aa:2" by fast
1265  qed
1266qed

1269AOT_theorem "approx-cont:1": ‹∃F∃G ◇(F ≈⇩E G & ◇¬F ≈⇩E G)›
1270proof -
1271  let ?P = ‹«[λx E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x]»›
1272  AOT_have ‹◇q⇩0 & ◇¬q⇩0› by (metis q⇩0_prop)
1273  AOT_hence 1: ‹◇∃x(E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x) & ◇¬∃x(E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x)›
1274    by (rule q⇩0_def[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(2), rotated])
1275       (simp add: "log-prop-prop:2")
1276  AOT_have θ: ‹◇∃x [«?P»]x & ◇¬∃x [«?P»]x›
1277    apply (AOT_subst ‹[«?P»]x› ‹E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x› bound: x)
1278     apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
1279    by (fact 1)
1280  show ?thesis
1281  proof (rule "∃I"(1))+
1282    AOT_have ‹◇[L]⇧- ≈⇩E [«?P»] & ◇¬[L]⇧- ≈⇩E [«?P»]›
1283    proof (rule "&I"; rule "RM◇"[THEN "→E"]; (rule "→I")?)
1284      AOT_modally_strict {
1285        AOT_assume A: ‹¬∃x [«?P»]x›
1286        AOT_show ‹[L]⇧- ≈⇩E [«?P»]›
1287        proof (safe intro!: "empty-approx:1"[unvarify F H, THEN "→E"] "rel-neg-T:3" "&I")
1288          AOT_show ‹[«?P»]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1289        next
1290          AOT_show ‹¬∃u [L⇧-]u›
1291          proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
1292            AOT_assume ‹∃u [L⇧-]u›
1293            then AOT_obtain u where ‹[L⇧-]u› using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by blast
1294            moreover AOT_have ‹¬[L⇧-]u›
1295              using "thm-noncont-e-e:2"[THEN "contingent-properties:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2)]
1296              by (metis "qml:2" "rule-ui:3" "vdash-properties:10" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
1297            ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p by (metis  "raa-cor:3")
1298          qed
1299        next

1464AOT_define eqE :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (infixl ‹≡⇩E› 50)
1465  eqE: ‹F ≡⇩E G ≡⇩d⇩f F↓ & G↓ & ∀u ([F]u ≡ [G]u)›
1466
1467AOT_theorem "apE-eqE:1": ‹F ≡⇩E G → F ≈⇩E G›
1468proof(rule "→I")
1469  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≡⇩E G›
1470  AOT_have ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1471  proof (safe intro!: "∃I"(1)[where τ="«(=⇩E)»"] "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "=E[denotes]" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I" "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
1472    fix u
1473    AOT_assume Fu: ‹[F]u›
1474    AOT_hence Gu: ‹[G]u›
1475      using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF eqE, OF 0, THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=u], THEN "≡E"(1)]
1476            Ordinary.ψ Fu by blast
1477    AOT_show ‹∃v ([G]v & u =⇩E v & ∀v' ([G]v' & u =⇩E v' → v' =⇩E v))›
1478      by (safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u] "&I" GEN "→I" Ordinary.ψ Gu "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Ordinary.ψ] "ord=Eequiv:2"[THEN "→E"] dest!: "&E"(2))
1479  next
1480    fix v
1481    AOT_assume Gv: ‹[G]v›
1482    AOT_hence Fv: ‹[F]v›
1483      using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF eqE, OF 0, THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=v], THEN "≡E"(2)]
1484            Ordinary.ψ Gv by blast
1485    AOT_show ‹∃u ([F]u & u =⇩E v & ∀v' ([F]v' & v' =⇩E v → v' =⇩E u))›
1486      by (safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=v] "&I" GEN "→I" Ordinary.ψ Fv "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Ordinary.ψ] "ord=Eequiv:2"[THEN "→E"] dest!: "&E"(2))
1487  qed
1488  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1489    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
1490qed
1491
1492AOT_theorem "apE-eqE:2": ‹(F ≈⇩E G & G ≡⇩E H) → F ≈⇩E H›
1493proof(rule "→I")
1494  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G & G ≡⇩E H›
1495  AOT_hence ‹F ≈⇩E G› and ‹G ≈⇩E H›
1496    using "apE-eqE:1"[THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast+
1497  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E H›
1498    by (metis Adjunction "eq-part:3" "vdash-properties:10")
1499qed

1518AOT_theorem "actuallyF:1": ‹❙𝒜(F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
1519proof -
1520  AOT_have 1: ‹❙𝒜([F]x ≡ ❙𝒜[F]x)› for x
1521    by (meson "Act-Basic:5" "act-conj-act:4" "≡E"(2) "Commutativity of ≡")
1522  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([F]x ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]x)› for x
1523    apply (AOT_subst ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]x› ‹❙𝒜[F]x›)
1524     apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
1525     apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
1526    by (fact 1)
1527  AOT_hence ‹O!x → ❙𝒜([F]x ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]x)› for x by (metis "deduction-theorem") 
1528  AOT_hence ‹∀u ❙𝒜([F]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u)›
1529    using "∀I" by fast
1530  AOT_hence 1: ‹❙𝒜∀u ([F]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u)›
1531    by (metis "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[2]" "vdash-properties:10")
1532  AOT_modally_strict {
1533    AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1534  } note 2 = this
1535  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(F ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
1536    apply (AOT_subst ‹F ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]› ‹∀u ([F]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u)›)
1537    using eqE[THEN "≡Df", THEN "≡S"(1), OF "&I", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst], OF 2]
1538    by (auto simp: 1)
1539  (* TODO: PLM: refers to a rule of substitution, which is not applicable *)
1540  moreover AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(F ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] → F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
1541    using "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify G, THEN "RA[2]", OF 2] by metis
1542  ultimately AOT_show ‹❙𝒜F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]›
1543    by (metis "act-cond" "vdash-properties:10")
1544qed

1567AOT_theorem "approx-nec:1": ‹Rigid(F) → F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]›
1568proof(rule "→I")
1569  AOT_assume ‹Rigid([F])›
1570  AOT_hence A: ‹□∀x ([F]x → □[F]x)›
1571    using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast
1572  AOT_hence 0: ‹∀x □([F]x → □[F]x)› using CBF[THEN "→E"] by blast
1573  AOT_hence 1: ‹∀x ([F]x → □[F]x)› using A "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"] by blast
1574  AOT_have act_F_den: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1575  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]›
1576  proof (safe intro!: "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify G, THEN "→E"] eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] act_F_den Ordinary.GEN "→I" "≡I")
1577    fix u
1578    AOT_assume ‹[F]u›
1579    AOT_hence ‹□[F]u› using 1[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
1580    AOT_hence act_F_u: ‹❙𝒜[F]u› by (metis "nec-imp-act" "vdash-properties:10")
1581    AOT_show ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u›
1582      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" act_F_u)
1583  next
1584    fix u
1585    AOT_assume ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u›
1586    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[F]u›
1587      by (rule "β→C"(1))
1588    AOT_thus ‹[F]u›
1589      using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)]
1590      by (metis "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-fur:2" "vdash-properties:10")
1591  qed
1592qed

1595AOT_theorem "approx-nec:2": ‹F ≈⇩E G ≡ ∀H ([λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G)›
1596proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
1597  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1598  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1599  AOT_hence ‹∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
1600    using "eq-part:4"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF 0] by blast
1601  AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G› for H
1602    by (rule "∀E"(1)[OF "eq-part:4"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF 0]]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
1603  AOT_thus ‹∀H ([λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G)› by (rule GEN)
1604next
1605  AOT_assume 0: ‹∀H ([λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G)›
1606  AOT_obtain H where ‹Rigidifies(H,F)› using "rigid-der:3" "∃E" by metis
1607  AOT_hence H: ‹Rigid(H) & ∀x ([H]x ≡ [F]x)›
1608    using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1609  AOT_have H_rigid: ‹□∀x ([H]x → □[H]x)› using H[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2)].
1610  AOT_hence ‹∀x □([H]x → □[H]x)›
1611    using "CBF" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
1612  AOT_hence ‹□([H]x → □[H]x)› for x using "∀E"(2) by blast
1613  AOT_hence rigid: ‹[H]x ≡ ❙𝒜[H]x› for x
1614     by (metis "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a" "sc-eq-fur:2" "vdash-properties:10")
1615  AOT_have ‹H ≡⇩E F›
1616  proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1617    AOT_show ‹[H]u ≡ [F]u› for u using H[THEN "&E"(2)] "∀E"(2) by fast
1618  qed
1619  AOT_hence ‹H ≈⇩E F›
1620    by (rule "apE-eqE:2"[THEN "→E", OF "&I", rotated])
1621       (simp add: "eq-part:1")
1622  AOT_hence F_approx_H: ‹F ≈⇩E H›
1623    by (metis "eq-part:2" "vdash-properties:10")
1624  moreover AOT_have H_eq_act_H: ‹H ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]›
1625  proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1626    AOT_show ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1627  next
1628    AOT_show ‹[H]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]u› for u
1629      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z]u› ‹❙𝒜[H]u›)
1630       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
1631       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
1632      using rigid by blast
1633  qed
1634  AOT_have a: ‹F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]›
1635    apply (rule "apE-eqE:2"[unvarify H, THEN "→E"])
1636     apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
1637    using F_approx_H H_eq_act_H "&I" by blast
1638  AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F›
1639    apply (rule "eq-part:2"[unvarify G, THEN "→E", rotated])
1640    by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1641  AOT_hence b: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G›
1642    by (rule 0[THEN "∀E"(1), THEN "≡E"(1), rotated]) (rule "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]) 
1643  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1644    by (rule "eq-part:3"[unvarify G, THEN "→E", rotated, OF "&I", OF a, OF b])
1645       "cqt:2[lambda]"
1646qed

1648AOT_theorem "approx-nec:3": ‹(Rigid(F) & Rigid(G)) → □(F ≈⇩E G → □F ≈⇩E G)›
1649proof (rule "→I")
1650  AOT_assume ‹Rigid(F) & Rigid(G)›
1651  AOT_hence ‹□∀x([F]x → □[F]x)› and ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x)›
1652    using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] "&E" by blast+
1653  AOT_hence ‹□(□∀x([F]x → □[F]x) & □∀x([G]x → □[G]x))›
1654    using "KBasic:3" "4" "&I" "≡E"(2) "vdash-properties:10" by meson
1655  moreover AOT_have ‹□(□∀x([F]x → □[F]x) & □∀x([G]x → □[G]x)) → □(F ≈⇩E G → □F ≈⇩E G)›
1656  proof(rule RM; rule "→I"; rule "→I")
1657    AOT_modally_strict {
1658      AOT_assume ‹□∀x([F]x → □[F]x) & □∀x([G]x → □[G]x)›
1659      AOT_hence ‹□∀x([F]x → □[F]x)› and ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x)› using "&E" by blast+
1660      AOT_hence ‹∀x□([F]x → □[F]x)› and ‹∀x□([G]x → □[G]x)› using CBF[THEN "→E"] by blast+
1661      AOT_hence F_nec: ‹□([F]x → □[F]x)› and G_nec: ‹□([G]x → □[G]x)› for x using "∀E"(2) by blast+
1662      AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1663      AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1664        by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "equi:3")
1665      then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1666      AOT_hence C1: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))› and C2: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
1667        using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
1668      AOT_obtain R' where ‹Rigidifies(R', R)›
1669        using "rigid-der:3" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1670      AOT_hence 1: ‹Rigid(R') & ∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([R']x⇩1...x⇩n ≡ [R]x⇩1...x⇩n)› using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1671      AOT_hence ‹□∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([R']x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R']x⇩1...x⇩n)› using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
1672      AOT_hence ‹∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n (◇[R']x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R']x⇩1...x⇩n)›
1673        using "≡E"(1) "rigid-rel-thms:1" by blast
1674      AOT_hence D: ‹∀x⇩1∀x⇩2 (◇[R']x⇩1x⇩2 → □[R']x⇩1x⇩2)›
1675        using tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1676      AOT_have E: ‹∀x⇩1∀x⇩2 ([R']x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [R]x⇩1x⇩2)› using tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF 1[THEN "&E"(2)]] by blast
1677      AOT_have ‹∀u □([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))› and ‹∀v □([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
1678      proof (safe intro!: Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1679        fix u
1680        AOT_show ‹□([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1681        proof (rule "raa-cor:1")
1682          AOT_assume ‹¬□([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1683          AOT_hence 1: ‹◇¬([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))› using "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1) by blast
1684          AOT_have ‹◇([F]u & ¬∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1685            apply (AOT_subst ‹[F]u & ¬∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)› ‹¬([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›)
1686             apply (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
1687            by (fact 1)
1688          AOT_hence A: ‹◇[F]u & ◇¬∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
1689            using "KBasic2:3" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
1690          AOT_hence ‹□[F]u›
1691            using F_nec "&E"(1) "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-box-box:1" "vdash-properties:6" by blast
1692          AOT_hence ‹[F]u› by (metis "qml:2" "vdash-properties:10" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
1693          AOT_hence ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)› using C1[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E"] by blast
1694          AOT_hence ‹∃v ([G]v & [R]uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
1695            using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by auto
1696          then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹O!a & ([G]a & [R]ua & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E a))›
1697            using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1698          AOT_have ‹∃v □([G]v & [R']uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
1699          proof(safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=a] "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "KBasic:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
1700            AOT_show ‹□[G]a›
1701              using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
1702              by (metis G_nec "qml:2" "vdash-properties:10" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
1703          next
1704            AOT_show ‹□[R']ua›
1705              using D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
1706                    E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(2),
1707                      OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]]
1708              by (metis "T◇" "vdash-properties:10")
1709          next
1710            AOT_have ‹∀v' □([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›
1711            proof (rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "raa-cor:1")
1712              fix v'
1713              AOT_assume ‹¬□([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›
1714              AOT_hence 1: ‹◇¬([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)› by (metis "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1))
1715              AOT_have ‹◇([G]v' & [R']uv' & ¬v' =⇩E a)›
1716                apply (AOT_subst ‹[G]v' & [R']uv' & ¬v' =⇩E a› ‹¬([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›)
1717                 apply (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
1718                by (fact 1)
1719              AOT_hence 1: ‹◇[G]v'› and 2: ‹◇[R']uv'› and 3: ‹◇¬v' =⇩E a›
1720                using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(1)] "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast+
1721              AOT_have Gv': ‹[G]v'› using G_nec 1
1722                by (meson "B◇" "KBasic:13" "vdash-properties:10")
1723              AOT_have ‹□[R']uv'› using 2 D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
1724              AOT_hence R'uv': ‹[R']uv'› by (metis "B◇" "T◇" "vdash-properties:10") 
1725              AOT_hence ‹[R]uv'› using E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
1726              AOT_hence ‹v' =⇩E a›
1727                using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E",
1728                             THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF Gv'] by blast
1729              AOT_hence ‹□(v' =⇩E a)› by (metis "id-nec3:1" "≡E"(4) "raa-cor:3")
1730              moreover AOT_have ‹¬□(v' =⇩E a)›
1731                using 3 "KBasic:11" "≡E"(2) by blast
1732              ultimately AOT_show ‹□(v' =⇩E a) & ¬□(v' =⇩E a)› using "&I" by blast
1733            qed
1734            AOT_thus ‹□∀v'([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›
1735              using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
1736          qed
1737          AOT_hence 1: ‹□∃v ([G]v & [R']uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
1738            using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[Buridan]" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
1739          AOT_have ‹□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
1740            by (AOT_subst ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)› ‹∃v ([G]v & [R']uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E v))›)
1741               (auto simp: 1 "equi:1")
1742          moreover AOT_have ‹¬□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
1743            using A[THEN "&E"(2)] "KBasic:11"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
1744          ultimately AOT_show ‹□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv) & ¬□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)› by (rule "&I")
1745        qed
1746      next
1747        fix v
1748        AOT_show ‹□([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
1749        proof (rule "raa-cor:1")
1750          AOT_assume ‹¬□([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
1751          AOT_hence 1: ‹◇¬([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))› using "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1) by blast
1752          AOT_have ‹◇([G]v & ¬∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
1753            apply (AOT_subst ‹[G]v & ¬∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)› ‹¬([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›)
1754             apply (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
1755            by (fact 1)
1756          AOT_hence A: ‹◇[G]v & ◇¬∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
1757            using "KBasic2:3" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
1758          AOT_hence ‹□[G]v›
1759            using G_nec "&E"(1) "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-box-box:1" "vdash-properties:6" by blast
1760          AOT_hence ‹[G]v› by (metis "qml:2" "vdash-properties:10" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
1761          AOT_hence ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv)› using C2[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E"] by blast
1762          AOT_hence ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uv & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R]u'v → u' =⇩E u))›
1763            using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by auto
1764          then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹O!a & ([F]a & [R]av & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R]u'v → u' =⇩E a))›
1765            using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1766          AOT_have ‹∃u □([F]u & [R']uv & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E u))›
1767          proof(safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=a] "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "KBasic:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
1768            AOT_show ‹□[F]a›
1769              using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
1770              by (metis F_nec "qml:2" "vdash-properties:10" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
1771          next
1772            AOT_show ‹□[R']av›
1773              using D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
1774                    E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(2),
1775                      OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]]
1776              by (metis "T◇" "vdash-properties:10")
1777          next
1778            AOT_have ‹∀u' □([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›
1779            proof (rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "raa-cor:1")
1780              fix u'
1781              AOT_assume ‹¬□([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›
1782              AOT_hence 1: ‹◇¬([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)› by (metis "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1))
1783              AOT_have ‹◇([F]u' & [R']u'v & ¬u' =⇩E a)›
1784                apply (AOT_subst ‹[F]u' & [R']u'v & ¬u' =⇩E a› ‹¬([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›)
1785                 apply (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
1786                by (fact 1)
1787              AOT_hence 1: ‹◇[F]u'› and 2: ‹◇[R']u'v› and 3: ‹◇¬u' =⇩E a›
1788                using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(1)] "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast+
1789              AOT_have Fu': ‹[F]u'› using F_nec 1
1790                by (meson "B◇" "KBasic:13" "vdash-properties:10")
1791              AOT_have ‹□[R']u'v› using 2 D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
1792              AOT_hence R'u'v: ‹[R']u'v› by (metis "B◇" "T◇" "vdash-properties:10") 
1793              AOT_hence ‹[R]u'v› using E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
1794              AOT_hence ‹u' =⇩E a›
1795                using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E",
1796                             THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF Fu'] by blast
1797              AOT_hence ‹□(u' =⇩E a)› by (metis "id-nec3:1" "≡E"(4) "raa-cor:3")
1798              moreover AOT_have ‹¬□(u' =⇩E a)›
1799                using 3 "KBasic:11" "≡E"(2) by blast
1800              ultimately AOT_show ‹□(u' =⇩E a) & ¬□(u' =⇩E a)› using "&I" by blast
1801            qed
1802            AOT_thus ‹□∀u'([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›
1803              using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
1804          qed
1805          AOT_hence 1: ‹□∃u ([F]u & [R']uv & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E u))›
1806            using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[Buridan]" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
1807          AOT_have ‹□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
1808            by (AOT_subst ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)› ‹∃u ([F]u & [R']uv & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E u))›)
1809               (auto simp: 1 "equi:1")
1810          moreover AOT_have ‹¬□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
1811            using A[THEN "&E"(2)] "KBasic:11"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
1812          ultimately AOT_show ‹□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv) & ¬□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)› by (rule "&I")
1813        qed
1814      qed
1815      AOT_hence ‹□∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))› and ‹□∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
1816        using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]"[THEN "→E"] by auto
1817      moreover AOT_have ‹□[R']↓› and ‹□[F]↓› and ‹□[G]↓›
1818        by (simp_all add: "ex:2:a")
1819      ultimately AOT_have 1: ‹□([R']↓ & [F]↓ & [G]↓ & ∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)) & ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)))›
1820        using "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(2) by meson
1821      AOT_have ‹□R' |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1822        by (AOT_subst_using subst: "equi:2"[THEN "≡Df"])
1823           (fact 1)
1824      AOT_hence ‹∃R □R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1825        by (rule "∃I"(2))
1826      AOT_hence 1: ‹□∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1827        by (metis Buridan "vdash-properties:10")
1828      AOT_show ‹□F ≈⇩E G›
1829        by (AOT_subst_using subst: "equi:3"[THEN "≡Df"])
1830           (fact 1)
1831    }
1832  qed
1833  ultimately AOT_show ‹□(F ≈⇩E G → □F ≈⇩E G)› using "→E" by blast
1834qed
1835

1837AOT_define numbers :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹Numbers'(_,_')›)
1838  ‹Numbers(x,G) ≡⇩d⇩f A!x & G↓ & ∀F(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
1839
1840AOT_theorem "numbers[den]":
1841  ‹Π↓ → (Numbers(κ, Π) ≡ A!κ & ∀F(κ[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E Π))›
1842  apply (safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "≡I" "→I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] dest!:  numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"])
1843  using "&E" by blast+

1845AOT_theorem "num-tran:1": ‹G ≈⇩E H → (Numbers(x, G) ≡ Numbers(x, H))›
1846proof (safe intro!: "→I" "≡I")
1847  AOT_assume 0: ‹G ≈⇩E H›
1848  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
1849  AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› and θ: ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
1850    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
1851  AOT_show ‹Numbers(x, H)›
1852  proof(safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" Ax "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] GEN)
1853    fix F
1854    AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› using θ[THEN "∀E"(2)].
1855    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H› using 0 "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2)] by metis
1856    finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H›.
1857  qed
1858next
1859  AOT_assume ‹G ≈⇩E H›
1860  AOT_hence 0: ‹H ≈⇩E G› by (metis "eq-part:2" "vdash-properties:10")
1861  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, H)›
1862  AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› and θ: ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H)›
1863    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
1864  AOT_show ‹Numbers(x, G)›
1865  proof(safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" Ax "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] GEN)
1866    fix F
1867    AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H› using θ[THEN "∀E"(2)].
1868    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› using 0 "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2)] by metis
1869    finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›.
1870  qed
1871qed

1873AOT_theorem "num-tran:2": ‹(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,H)) → G ≈⇩E H›
1874proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
1875  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x,G)›
1876  AOT_hence ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
1877  AOT_hence 1: ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› for F using "∀E"(2) by blast
1878  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x,H)›
1879  AOT_hence ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H)› using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
1880  AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H› for F using "∀E"(2) by blast
1881  AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H› for F by (metis "1" "≡E"(6))
1882  AOT_thus ‹G ≈⇩E H›
1883    using "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(2), OF GEN] by blast
1884qed

1886AOT_theorem "num-tran:3": ‹G ≡⇩E H → (Numbers(x, G) ≡ Numbers(x, H))›
1887  using "apE-eqE:1" "Hypothetical Syllogism" "num-tran:1" by blast

1889AOT_theorem "pre-Hume": ‹(Numbers(x,G) & Numbers(y,H)) → (x = y ≡ G ≈⇩E H)›
1890proof(safe intro!: "→I" "≡I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
1891  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
1892  moreover AOT_assume ‹x = y›
1893  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(y, G)› by (rule "rule=E")
1894  moreover AOT_assume ‹Numbers(y, H)›
1895  ultimately AOT_show ‹G ≈⇩E H› using "num-tran:2" "→E" "&I" by blast
1896next
1897  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
1898  AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› and xF: ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
1899  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(y, H)›
1900  AOT_hence Ay: ‹A!y› and yF: ‹∀F (y[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H)› using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
1901  AOT_assume G_approx_H: ‹G ≈⇩E H›
1902  AOT_show ‹x = y›
1903  proof(rule "ab-obey:1"[THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF Ax, OF Ay]; rule GEN)
1904    fix F
1905    AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› using xF[THEN "∀E"(2)].
1906    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H› using "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF G_approx_H, THEN "∀E"(2)].
1907    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ y[F]› using yF[THEN "∀E"(2), symmetric].
1908    finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ y[F]›.
1909  qed
1910qed

1912AOT_theorem "two-num-not": ‹∃u∃v(u ≠ v) → ∃x∃G∃H(Numbers(x,G) & Numbers(x, H) & ¬G ≡⇩E H)›
1913proof (rule "→I")
1914  AOT_have eqE_den: ‹[λx x =⇩E y]↓› for y by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1915  AOT_assume ‹∃u∃v(u ≠ v)›
1916  then AOT_obtain c where Oc: ‹O!c› and ‹∃v (c ≠ v)› using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1917  then AOT_obtain d where Od: ‹O!d› and c_noteq_d: ‹c ≠ d› using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1918  AOT_hence c_noteqE_d: ‹c ≠⇩E d›
1919    using "=E-simple:2"[THEN "→E"] "=E-simple:2" "≡E"(2) "modus-tollens:1" "=-infix" "≡⇩d⇩fE" "thm-neg=E" by fast
1920  AOT_hence not_c_eqE_d: ‹¬c =⇩E d›
1921    using "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E" by blast
1922  AOT_have ‹∃x (A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E c]))›
1923    by (simp add: "A-objects" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
1924  then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹A!a & ∀F (a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E c])› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1925  AOT_have ‹∃x (A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]))›
1926    by (simp add: "A-objects" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
1927  then AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹A!b & ∀F (b[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E d])› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1928  AOT_have num_a_eq_c: ‹Numbers(a, [λx x =⇩E c])›
1929    by (safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] a_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
1930  moreover AOT_have num_b_eq_d: ‹Numbers(b, [λx x =⇩E d])›
1931    by (safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] b_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
1932  moreover AOT_have ‹[λx x =⇩E c] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
1933  proof (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
1934    let ?R = ‹«[λxy (x =⇩E c & y =⇩E d)]»›
1935    AOT_have Rcd: ‹[«?R»]cd›
1936      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" prod_denotesI "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E"] Od Oc)
1937    AOT_show ‹∃R R |: [λx x =⇩E c] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
1938    proof (safe intro!: "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹?R›] "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" eqE_den Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1939      AOT_show ‹«?R»↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1940    next
1941      fix u
1942      AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E c]u›
1943      AOT_hence ‹u =⇩E c› by (metis "β→C"(1))
1944      AOT_hence u_is_c: ‹u = c›  by (metis "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:6")
1945      AOT_show ‹∃!v ([λx x =⇩E d]v & [«?R»]uv)›
1946      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=d] "&I" Od Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1947        AOT_show ‹[λx x =⇩E d]d›
1948          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Od])
1949      next
1950        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]ud› using u_is_c[symmetric] Rcd "rule=E" by fast
1951      next
1952        fix v
1953        AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E d]v & [«?R»]uv›
1954        AOT_thus ‹v =⇩E d› by (metis "β→C"(1) "&E"(1))
1955      qed
1956    next
1957      fix v
1958      AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E d]v›
1959      AOT_hence ‹v =⇩E d› by (metis "β→C"(1))
1960      AOT_hence v_is_d: ‹v = d›  by (metis "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:6")
1961      AOT_show ‹∃!u ([λx x =⇩E c]u & [«?R»]uv)›
1962      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=c] "&I" Oc Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1963        AOT_show ‹[λx x =⇩E c]c›
1964          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Oc])
1965      next
1966        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]cv› using v_is_d[symmetric] Rcd "rule=E" by fast
1967      next
1968        fix u
1969        AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E c]u & [«?R»]uv›
1970        AOT_thus ‹u =⇩E c› by (metis "β→C"(1) "&E"(1))
1971      qed
1972    next
1973      AOT_show ‹«?R»↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1974    qed
1975  qed
1976  ultimately AOT_have ‹a = b›
1977    using  "pre-Hume"[unvarify G H, OF eqE_den, OF eqE_den, THEN "→E", OF "&I", THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
1978  AOT_hence num_a_eq_d: ‹Numbers(a, [λx x =⇩E d])› using num_b_eq_d "rule=E" id_sym by fast
1979  AOT_have not_equiv: ‹¬[λx x =⇩E c] ≡⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
1980  proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
1981    AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E c] ≡⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
1982    AOT_hence ‹[λx x =⇩E c]c ≡ [λx x =⇩E d]c› using eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] Oc by blast
1983    moreover AOT_have ‹[λx x =⇩E c]c›
1984      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Oc])
1985    ultimately AOT_have ‹[λx x =⇩E d]c› using "≡E"(1) by blast
1986    AOT_hence ‹c =⇩E d›
1987      by (rule "β→C"(1))
1988    AOT_thus ‹c =⇩E d & ¬c =⇩E d› using not_c_eqE_d "&I" by blast
1989  qed
1990  AOT_show ‹∃x ∃G ∃H (Numbers(x,G) & Numbers(x,H) & ¬G ≡⇩E H)›
1991    apply (rule "∃I"(2)[where β=a])
1992    apply (rule "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«[λx x =⇩E c]»›])
1993     apply (rule "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«[λx x =⇩E d]»›])
1994    by (safe intro!: eqE_den "&I" num_a_eq_c num_a_eq_d not_equiv)
1995qed

1999     (auto simp: "numbers[den]"[THEN "→E", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]] "A-objects"[axiom_inst])

2005AOT_theorem "num-cont:1": ‹∃x∃G(Numbers(x, G) & ¬□Numbers(x, G))›
2006proof -
2007  AOT_have ‹∃F∃G ◇([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G & ◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2008    using "approx-cont:2".
2009  then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃G ◇([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G & ◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2010  then AOT_obtain G where ‹◇([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G & ◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2011  AOT_hence θ: ‹◇[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› and ζ: ‹◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›
2012    using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E"] "&E" "4◇"[THEN "→E"] by blast+
2013  AOT_obtain a where ‹Numbers(a, G)› using "num:1" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2014  moreover AOT_have ‹¬□Numbers(a, G)›
2015  proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
2016    AOT_assume 1: ‹□Numbers(a, G)›
2017    AOT_have ‹□([A!]a & G↓ & ∀F (a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2018      by (AOT_subst_using_rev subst: numbers[THEN "≡Df"]) (fact 1)
2019    AOT_hence ‹□A!a› and ‹□∀F (a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2020      using "KBasic:3"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "&E" by blast+
2021    AOT_hence ‹∀F □(a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using CBF[THEN "→E"] by blast
2022    AOT_hence ‹□(a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using "∀E"(2) by blast
2023    AOT_hence A: ‹□(a[F] → [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› and B: ‹□([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → a[F])›
2024      using "KBasic:4"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "&E" by blast+
2025    AOT_have ‹□(¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → ¬a[F])›
2026      apply (AOT_subst ‹¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → ¬a[F]› ‹a[F] → [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›)
2027       using "≡I" "useful-tautologies:4" "useful-tautologies:5" apply presburger
2028       by (fact A)
2029    AOT_hence ‹◇¬a[F]› by (metis "KBasic:13" ζ "vdash-properties:10")
2030    AOT_hence ‹¬a[F]› by (metis "KBasic:11" "en-eq:2[1]" "≡E"(2) "≡E"(4))
2031    AOT_hence ‹¬◇a[F]› by (metis "en-eq:3[1]" "≡E"(4))
2032    moreover AOT_have ‹◇a[F]› by (meson B θ "KBasic:13" "vdash-properties:10")
2033    ultimately AOT_show ‹◇a[F] & ¬◇a[F]› using "&I" by blast
2034  qed
2035
2036  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(a, G) & ¬□Numbers(a, G)› using "&I" by blast
2037  AOT_hence ‹∃G (Numbers(a, G) & ¬□Numbers(a, G))› by (rule "∃I")
2038  AOT_thus ‹∃x∃G (Numbers(x, G) & ¬□Numbers(x, G))› by (rule "∃I")
2039qed

2041AOT_theorem "num-cont:2": ‹Rigid(G) → □∀x(Numbers(x,G) → □Numbers(x,G))›
2042proof(rule "→I")
2043  AOT_assume ‹Rigid(G)›
2044  AOT_hence ‹□∀z([G]z → □[G]z)›
2045    using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast
2046  AOT_hence ‹□□∀z([G]z → □[G]z)› by (metis "S5Basic:6" "≡E"(1))
2047  moreover AOT_have ‹□□∀z([G]z → □[G]z) → □∀x(Numbers(x,G) → □Numbers(x,G))›
2048  proof(rule RM; safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
2049    AOT_modally_strict {
2050      AOT_have act_den: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2051      fix x
2052      AOT_assume G_nec: ‹□∀z([G]z → □[G]z)›
2053      AOT_hence G_rigid: ‹Rigid(G)›
2054        using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI", OF "&I", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]]
2055        by blast
2056      AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2057      AOT_hence ‹[A!]x & G↓ & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2058      AOT_hence Ax: ‹[A!]x› and ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using "&E" by blast+
2059      AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› for F using "∀E"(2) by blast
2060      moreover AOT_have ‹□([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → □[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› for F
2061        using "approx-nec:3"[unvarify F, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "actuallyF:2", OF G_rigid].
2062      moreover AOT_have ‹□(x[F] → □x[F])› for F by (simp add: RN "pre-en-eq:1[1]")
2063      ultimately AOT_have ‹□(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› for F
2064        using "sc-eq-box-box:5" "→E" "qml:2"[axiom_inst] "&I" by meson
2065      AOT_hence ‹∀F □(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› by (rule "∀I")
2066      AOT_hence 1: ‹□∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› using BF[THEN "→E"] by fast
2067      AOT_have ‹□G↓› by (simp add: "ex:2:a")
2068      moreover AOT_have ‹□[A!]x› using Ax using "oa-facts:2" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
2069      ultimately AOT_have ‹□(A!x & G↓)›
2070        by (metis "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(2))
2071      AOT_hence 2: ‹□(A!x & G↓ & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))› using 1
2072        using "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(2) by fast
2073      AOT_show ‹□Numbers(x, G)›
2074        by (AOT_subst_using subst: numbers[THEN "≡Df"]) (fact 2)
2075    }
2076  qed
2077  ultimately AOT_show ‹□∀x(Numbers(x,G) → □Numbers(x,G))›
2078    using "→E" by blast
2079qed

2083      ("cqt:2[lambda]" | rule "actuallyF:2"))

2094AOT_theorem "num-can:1": ‹#G = ❙ιx(A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›

2098  AOT_hence ‹❙ιx Numbers(x, G) = ❙ιx([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›

2104AOT_theorem "num-can:2": ‹#G = ❙ιx(A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2105proof (rule id_trans[OF "num-can:1"]; rule "equiv-desc-eq:2"[THEN "→E"];
2106       safe intro!: "&I" "A-descriptions" "logic-actual-nec:3"[axiom_inst, THEN "≡E"(2)]
2107                    GEN "Act-Basic:5"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
2108  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2109  AOT_have "eq-part:3[terms]": ‹❙⊢⇩□ F ≈⇩E G & F ≈⇩E H → G ≈⇩E H› for F G H
2110    by (metis "&I" "eq-part:2" "eq-part:3" "→I" "&E" "vdash-properties:6")
2111  fix x
2112  {
2113    fix F
2114    AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
2115      by (simp add: "actuallyF:1")
2116    moreover AOT_have ‹❙𝒜((F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]) → ([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2117      by (auto intro!: "RA[2]" "→I" "≡I"
2118               simp: "eq-part:3"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "&I"]
2119                     "eq-part:3[terms]"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "&I"])
2120    ultimately AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ F ≈⇩E G)›
2121      using "logic-actual-nec:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "≡E"(1), THEN "→E"] by blast
2122
2123    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ ❙𝒜F ≈⇩E G› by (metis "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(1))
2124    (* TODO: PLM: Important: cites 727.4 instead of 727.5 ; also missing parentheses? wrong citation? Next formula after θ. *)
2125    AOT_hence 0: ‹(❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ (❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜F ≈⇩E G)›
2126      by (auto intro!: "≡I" "→I" elim: "≡E")
2127    AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ (❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2128      by (simp add: "Act-Basic:5")
2129    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ (❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜F ≈⇩E G)› using 0.
2130    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜((x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2131      by (meson "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2132    finally AOT_have 0: ‹❙𝒜(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ ❙𝒜((x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›.
2133  } note 0 = this
2134  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ ∀F ❙𝒜(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2135    using "logic-actual-nec:3" "vdash-properties:1[2]" by blast
2136  also AOT_have ‹… ≡  ∀F ❙𝒜((x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2137    apply (safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" GEN)
2138    using 0 "≡E"(1) "≡E"(2) "rule-ui:3" by blast+
2139  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜(∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2140    using "≡E"(6) "logic-actual-nec:3" "oth-class-taut:3:a" "vdash-properties:1[2]" by blast
2141  finally AOT_have 0: ‹❙𝒜∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ ❙𝒜(∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›.
2142  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)) ≡ (❙𝒜A!x & ❙𝒜∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2143    by (simp add: "Act-Basic:2")
2144  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜[A!]x & ❙𝒜(∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2145    using 0 "oth-class-taut:4:f" "vdash-properties:6" by blast
2146  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜(A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2147    using "Act-Basic:2" "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a" by blast
2148  finally AOT_show ‹❙𝒜([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)) ≡ ❙𝒜([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›.
2149qed
