2151AOT_define NaturalCardinal :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹NaturalCardinal'(_')›)

2154AOT_theorem "natcard-nec": ‹NaturalCardinal(x) → □NaturalCardinal(x)›
2155proof(rule "→I")
2156  AOT_assume ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2157  AOT_hence ‹∃G(x = #G)› using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2158  then AOT_obtain G where ‹x = #G› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2159  AOT_hence ‹□x = #G› by (metis "id-nec:2" "vdash-properties:10")
2160  AOT_hence ‹∃G □x = #G› by (rule "∃I")
2161  AOT_hence 1: ‹□∃G x = #G› by (metis Buridan "vdash-properties:10")
2162  AOT_show ‹□NaturalCardinal(x)›
2163    by (AOT_subst_using subst: card[THEN "≡Df"]) (fact 1)
2164qed

2182AOT_theorem "hume-strict": ‹∃!x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G)) ≡ F ≈⇩E G›
2183proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2184  AOT_assume ‹∃!x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G))›
2185  AOT_hence ‹∃x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G) & ∀z ((Numbers(z, F) & Numbers(z, G) → z = x)))›
2186    using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2187  then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹Numbers(a, F) & Numbers(a, G) & ∀z ((Numbers(z, F) & Numbers(z, G) → z = a))›
2188    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2189  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E G›
2190    by (auto intro!: "id-eq:1" "pre-Hume"[THEN "→E", OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "≡E"(1)])
2191next
2192  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
2193  moreover AOT_obtain b where num_b_F: ‹Numbers(b, F)› by (metis "instantiation" "num:1")
2194  ultimately AOT_have num_b_G: ‹Numbers(b, G)› using "num-tran:1"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2195  AOT_have ‹∀z (Numbers(z, F) & Numbers(z, G) → z = b)›
2196  proof(safe intro!: GEN "→I"; drule "&E"(1))
2197    AOT_show ‹z = b› if ‹Numbers(z, F)› for z
2198      using "pre-Hume"[THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF that, OF num_b_F, THEN "≡E"(2), rotated, OF "eq-part:1"].
2199  qed
2200  AOT_hence ‹Numbers(b, F) & Numbers(b, G) & ∀z (Numbers(z, F) & Numbers(z, G) → z = b)›
2201    using num_b_F num_b_G "&I" by blast
2202  AOT_hence ‹∃x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G) & ∀z (Numbers(z, F) & Numbers(z, G) → z = x))›
2203    by (rule "∃I")
2204  AOT_thus ‹∃!x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G))›
2205    by (rule "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
2206qed

2208AOT_theorem unotEu: ‹¬∃y[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y›

2210  AOT_assume ‹∃y[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y›
2211  then AOT_obtain y where ‹[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2212  AOT_hence 0: ‹O!y & y ≠⇩E y› by (rule "β→C"(1))
2213  AOT_hence ‹¬(y =⇩E y)› using "&E"(2) "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E" by blast
2214  moreover AOT_have ‹y =⇩E y› by (metis 0[THEN "&E"(1)] "ord=Eequiv:1" "vdash-properties:10")
2215  ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p by (metis "raa-cor:3")
2216qed

2233AOT_theorem "eq-num:1": ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G) ≡ Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2234proof -
2235  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2236  AOT_have ‹□(∃!x(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])) ≡ G ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2237    using "hume-strict"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN RN].
2238  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜(∃!x(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])) ≡ G ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2239    using "nec-imp-act"[THEN "→E"] by fast
2240  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜(∃!x(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])))›
2241    using "actuallyF:1" "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(1) "≡E"(2) by fast
2242  AOT_hence ‹∃!x ❙𝒜((Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])))›
2243    by (metis "A-Exists:1" "≡E"(1))
2244  AOT_hence ‹∃x(❙𝒜((Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z]))) & ∀z(❙𝒜((Numbers(z, G) & Numbers(z,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z]))) → z = x))›
2245    using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2246  then AOT_obtain a where ‹❙𝒜((Numbers(a, G) & Numbers(a,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])))›
2247    using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
2248  AOT_hence act_a_num_G: ‹❙𝒜Numbers(a, G)› and act_a_num_actG: ‹❙𝒜Numbers(a,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2249    using "Act-Basic:2" "&E" "≡E"(1) by blast+
2250  AOT_hence num_a_act_g: ‹Numbers(a, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2251    using "num-cont:2"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "actuallyF:2",
2252                       THEN CBF[THEN "→E"], THEN "∀E"(2)]
2253    by (metis "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-fur:2" "vdash-properties:6")
2254  AOT_have 0: ‹❙⊢⇩□ Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(y, G) → x = y› for y
2255    using "pre-Hume"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2), rotated, OF "eq-part:1"] "→I" by blast
2256  show ?thesis
2257  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2258    AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G)›
2259    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜x = a›
2260      using 0[THEN "RA[2]", THEN "act-cond"[THEN "→E"], THEN "→E", OF "Act-Basic:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)], OF "&I"]
2261            act_a_num_G by blast
2262    AOT_hence ‹x = a› by (metis "id-act:1" "≡E"(2))
2263    AOT_hence ‹a = x› using id_sym by auto
2264    AOT_thus ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2265      using "rule=E" num_a_act_g by fast
2266  next
2267    AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2268    AOT_hence ‹a = x›
2269      using "pre-Hume"[unvarify G H, THEN "→E", OF act_den, OF act_den, OF "&I", OF num_a_act_g, THEN "≡E"(2)]
2270            "eq-part:1"[unvarify F, OF act_den] by blast
2271    AOT_thus ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G)›
2272      using act_a_num_G "rule=E" by fast
2273  qed
2274qed

2276AOT_theorem "eq-num:2": ‹Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ x = #G›
2277proof -
2278  AOT_have 0: ‹❙⊢⇩□ x = ❙ιx Numbers(x, G) ≡ ∀y (Numbers(y, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ y = x)› for x
2279    by (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])› ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G)› bound: x)
2280       (auto simp: "eq-num:1" descriptions[axiom_inst])
2281  AOT_have ‹#G = ❙ιx Numbers(x, G) ≡ ∀y (Numbers(y, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ y = #G)›
2282    using 0[unvarify x, OF "num-def:2"].
2283  moreover AOT_have ‹#G = ❙ιx Numbers(x, G)›
2284    using "num-def:1" "num-uniq" "rule-id-df:1" by blast
2285  ultimately AOT_have ‹∀y (Numbers(y, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ y = #G)› using "≡E" by blast
2286  thus ?thesis using "∀E"(2) by blast
2287qed

2311AOT_theorem "eq-num:6": ‹Numbers(x, G) → NaturalCardinal(x)›
2312proof(rule "→I")
2313  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2314  AOT_obtain F where ‹Rigidifies(F, G)›
2315    by (metis "instantiation" "rigid-der:3")
2316  AOT_hence θ: ‹Rigid(F)› and ‹∀x([F]x ≡ [G]x)›
2317    using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)]
2318          "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1)]
2319    by blast+
2320  AOT_hence ‹F ≡⇩E G›
2321    by (auto intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] GEN "→I" elim: "∀E"(2))
2322  moreover AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2323  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, F)›
2324    using "num-tran:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2325  moreover AOT_have ‹F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]› using θ "approx-nec:1" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
2326  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
2327    using "num-tran:1"[unvarify H, OF act_den, THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2328  AOT_hence ‹x = #F› using "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2329  AOT_hence ‹∃F x = #F› by (rule "∃I")
2330  AOT_thus ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2331    using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by blast
2332qed
2333
2334AOT_theorem "eq-df-num": ‹∃G (x = #G) ≡ ∃G (Numbers(x,G))›
2335proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2336  AOT_assume ‹∃G (x = #G)›
2337  then AOT_obtain P where ‹x = #P› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2338  AOT_hence ‹Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[P]z])›
2339    using "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2340  moreover AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[P]z]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2341  ultimately AOT_show ‹∃G(Numbers(x,G))› by (rule "∃I")
2342next
2343  AOT_assume ‹∃G (Numbers(x,G))›
2344  then AOT_obtain Q where ‹Numbers(x,Q)›
2345    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2346  AOT_hence ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2347    using "eq-num:6"[THEN "→E"] by blast
2348  AOT_thus ‹∃G (x = #G)›
2349    using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2350qed

2352AOT_theorem "card-en": ‹NaturalCardinal(x) → ∀F(x[F] ≡ x = #F)›
2353proof(rule "→I"; rule GEN)
2354  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2355  fix F
2356  AOT_assume ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2357  AOT_hence ‹∃F x = #F› using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2358  then AOT_obtain P where x_def: ‹x = #P› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2359  AOT_hence num_x_act_P: ‹Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[P]z])› using "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2360  AOT_have ‹#P[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[P]z]›
2361    using "eq-num:4"[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)] by blast
2362  AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[P]z]› using x_def[symmetric] "rule=E" by fast
2363  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
2364    using "num-tran:1"[unvarify G H, OF act_den, OF act_den]
2365    using "num-tran:2"[unvarify G H, OF act_den, OF act_den]
2366    by (metis "&I" "deduction-theorem" "≡I" "≡E"(2) num_x_act_P)
2367  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ x = #F›
2368    using "eq-num:2" by blast
2369  finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ x = #F›.
2370qed

2372AOT_theorem "0F:1": ‹¬∃u [F]u ≡ Numbers(0, F)›
2373proof -
2374  AOT_have unotEu_act_ord: ‹¬∃v[λx O!x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]v›
2375  proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
2376    AOT_assume ‹∃v[λx O!x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]v›
2377    then AOT_obtain y where ‹[λx O!x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]y› using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
2378    AOT_hence 0: ‹O!y & ❙𝒜y ≠⇩E y› by (rule "β→C"(1))
2379    AOT_have ‹❙𝒜¬(y =⇩E y)›
2380      apply (AOT_subst  ‹¬(y =⇩E y)› ‹y ≠⇩E y›)
2381       apply (meson "≡E"(2) "Commutativity of ≡" "thm-neg=E")
2382      by (fact 0[THEN "&E"(2)])
2383    AOT_hence ‹¬(y =⇩E y)› by (metis "¬¬I" "Act-Sub:1" "id-act2:1" "≡E"(4))
2384    moreover AOT_have ‹y =⇩E y› by (metis 0[THEN "&E"(1)] "ord=Eequiv:1" "vdash-properties:10")
2385    ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p by (metis "raa-cor:3")
2386  qed
2387  AOT_have ‹Numbers(0, [λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y])›
2388    apply (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(2)[OF "zero:1"])
2389     apply (rule "num-def:2"[unvarify G]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
2390    apply (rule "eq-num:3"[unvarify G])
2391    by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2392  AOT_hence numbers0: ‹Numbers(0, [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x])›
2393  proof (rule "num-tran:3"[unvarify x G H, THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1), rotated 4])
2394    AOT_show ‹[λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y] ≡⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]›
2395    proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" Ordinary.GEN "→I")
2396      fix u
2397      AOT_have ‹[λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y]u ≡ ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]u›
2398        by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
2399      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜(O!u & u ≠⇩E u)›
2400        apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]u› ‹O!u & u ≠⇩E u›)
2401         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
2402        by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2403      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ (❙𝒜O!u & ❙𝒜u ≠⇩E u)›
2404        by (simp add: "Act-Basic:2")
2405      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ (O!u & ❙𝒜u ≠⇩E u)›
2406        by (metis Ordinary.ψ "&I" "&E"(2) "deduction-theorem" "≡I" "≡E"(1) "oa-facts:7")
2407      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]u›
2408        by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", symmetric]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
2409      finally AOT_show ‹[λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y]u ≡ [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]u›.
2410    qed("cqt:2[lambda]")+
2411  qed(fact "zero:2" | "cqt:2[lambda]")+
2412  show ?thesis
2413  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2414    AOT_assume ‹¬∃u [F]u›
2415    moreover AOT_have ‹¬∃v [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]v› using unotEu_act_ord.
2416    ultimately AOT_have 0: ‹F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]›
2417      by (rule "empty-approx:1"[unvarify H, THEN "→E", rotated, OF "&I"]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
2418    AOT_thus ‹Numbers(0, F)›
2419      by (rule "num-tran:1"[unvarify x H, THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2), rotated, rotated])
2420         (fact "zero:2" numbers0 | "cqt:2[lambda]")+
2421  next
2422    AOT_assume ‹Numbers(0, F)›
2423    AOT_hence 1: ‹F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]›
2424      by (rule "num-tran:2"[unvarify x H, THEN "→E", rotated 2, OF "&I"])
2425         (fact numbers0 "zero:2" | "cqt:2[lambda]")+
2426    AOT_show ‹¬∃u [F]u›
2427    proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
2428      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2429      AOT_assume ‹∃u [F]u›
2430      AOT_hence ‹¬(F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x])›
2431        by (rule "empty-approx:2"[unvarify H, OF 0, THEN "→E", OF "&I"])
2432           (rule unotEu_act_ord)
2433      AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x] & ¬(F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x])› 
2434        using 1 "&I" by blast
2435    qed
2436  qed
2437qed

2467      by (auto intro!: "β←C" "cqt:2")

2494AOT_theorem "0F:4": ‹w ⊨ ¬∃u [F]u ≡ #[F]⇩w = 0›
2495proof (rule "rule-id-df:2:b"[OF "w-index", where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
2496  AOT_show ‹[λx⇩1...x⇩n w ⊨ [F]x⇩1...x⇩n]↓›
2497    by (simp add: "w-rel:3")
2498next
2499  AOT_show ‹w ⊨ ¬∃u [F]u ≡ #[λx w ⊨ [F]x] = 0›
2500  proof (rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
2501    AOT_assume ‹w ⊨ ¬∃u [F]u›
2502    AOT_hence 0: ‹¬w ⊨ ∃u [F]u›
2503      using "coherent:1"[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2504    AOT_have ‹¬∃u ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u›
2505    proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
2506      AOT_assume ‹∃u ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u›
2507      then AOT_obtain u where ‹❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u› using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
2508      AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜w ⊨ [F]u›
2509        by (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹w ⊨ [F]u› ‹[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u›; 
2510            safe intro!: "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"] "w-rel:1"[THEN "→E"])
2511           "cqt:2"
2512      AOT_hence 1: ‹w ⊨ [F]u›
2513        using "rigid-truth-at:4"[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2514      AOT_have ‹□O!u› by (simp add: Ordinary.restricted_var_condition RN)
2515      AOT_hence ‹∀w w ⊨ O!u›
2516        using "fund:2"[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2517      AOT_hence ‹w ⊨ O!u› by (metis "PossibleWorld.∀E")
2518      AOT_hence ‹w ⊨ (O!u & [F]u)›
2519        using "conj-dist-w:1"[unvarify p q, OF "log-prop-prop:2", OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(2)]
2520              "&I" 1 by blast
2521      AOT_hence ‹∃x w ⊨ (O!x & [F]x)› using "∃I" by fast
2522      AOT_hence ‹w ⊨ ∃u [F]u›
2523        using "conj-dist-w:6"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by fast
2524      AOT_thus ‹w ⊨ ∃u [F]u & ¬w ⊨ ∃u [F]u›
2525        using 0 "&I" by blast
2526    qed
2527    AOT_thus ‹#[λx w ⊨ [F]x] = 0›
2528      by (safe intro!: "0F:2"[unvarify F, THEN "≡E"(1)] "w-rel:1"[THEN "→E"])
2529         "cqt:2"
2530  next
2531    AOT_assume ‹#[λx w ⊨ [F]x] = 0›
2532    AOT_hence 0: ‹¬∃u ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u›
2533      by (safe intro!: "0F:2"[unvarify F, THEN "≡E"(2)] "w-rel:1"[THEN "→E"])
2534         "cqt:2"
2535    AOT_have ‹¬w ⊨ ∃u [F]u›
2536    proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
2537      AOT_assume ‹w ⊨ ∃u [F]u›
2538      AOT_hence ‹∃x w ⊨ (O!x & [F]x)›
2539        using "conj-dist-w:6"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by fast
2540      then AOT_obtain x where ‹w ⊨ (O!x & [F]x)› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2541      AOT_hence ‹w ⊨ O!x› and Fx_in_w: ‹w ⊨ [F]x›
2542        using "conj-dist-w:1"[unvarify p q] "≡E"(1) "log-prop-prop:2" "&E" by blast+
2543      AOT_hence ‹◇O!x›
2544        using "fund:1"[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(2)] "PossibleWorld.∃I" by simp
2545      AOT_hence ord_x: ‹O!x› using "oa-facts:3"[THEN "→E"] by blast
2546      AOT_have ‹❙𝒜w ⊨ [F]x›
2547        using "rigid-truth-at:4"[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(2)] Fx_in_w by blast
2548      AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]x›
2549        by (AOT_subst ‹[λx w ⊨ [F]x]x› ‹w ⊨ [F]x›; safe intro!: "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"] "w-rel:1"[THEN "→E"]) "cqt:2"
2550      AOT_hence ‹O!x & ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]x›
2551        using ord_x "&I" by blast
2552      AOT_hence ‹∃x (O!x & ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]x)› using "∃I" by fast
2553      AOT_thus ‹∃u (❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u) & ¬∃u ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u›
2554        using 0 "&I" by blast
2555    qed
2556    AOT_thus ‹w ⊨ ¬∃u[F]u›
2557      using "coherent:1"[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2558  qed
2559qed

2561AOT_act_theorem "zero=:1": ‹NaturalCardinal(x) → ∀F (x[F] ≡ Numbers(x, F))›
2562proof(safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
2563  fix F
2564  AOT_assume ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2565  AOT_hence ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ x = #F)› by (metis "card-en" "vdash-properties:10")
2566  AOT_hence 1: ‹x[F] ≡ x = #F› using "∀E"(2) by blast
2567  AOT_have 2: ‹x[F] ≡ x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F))›
2568    by (rule "num-def:1"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1)])
2569       (auto simp: 1 "num-uniq")
2570  AOT_have ‹x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F)) → Numbers(x, F)› (* TODO: PLM: missing closing parenthesis *)
2571    using "y-in:1" by blast
2572  moreover AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, F) → x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F))›
2573  proof(rule "→I")
2574    AOT_assume 1: ‹Numbers(x, F)›
2575    moreover AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹∀y (Numbers(y, F) → y = z)›
2576      using "num:2"[THEN "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"]] "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
2577    ultimately AOT_have ‹x = z› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
2578    AOT_hence ‹∀y (Numbers(y, F) → y = x)› using z_prop "rule=E" id_sym by fast
2579    AOT_thus ‹x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y,F))›
2580      by (rule hintikka[THEN "≡E"(2), OF "&I", rotated])
2581         (fact 1)
2582  qed
2583  ultimately AOT_have ‹x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F)) ≡ Numbers(x, F)›
2584    by (metis "≡I")
2585  AOT_thus ‹x[F] ≡ Numbers(x, F)› using 2 by (metis "≡E"(5))
2586qed
2587
2588AOT_act_theorem "zero=:2": ‹0[F] ≡ ¬∃u[F]u›
2589proof -
2590  AOT_have ‹0[F] ≡ Numbers(0, F)›
2591    using "zero=:1"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "→E", OF "zero-card", THEN "∀E"(2)].
2592  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ¬∃u[F]u› using "0F:1"[symmetric].
2593  finally show ?thesis.
2594qed

2596AOT_act_theorem "zero=:3": ‹¬∃u[F]u ≡ #F = 0›
2597proof -
2598  AOT_have ‹¬∃u[F]u ≡ 0[F]› using "zero=:2"[symmetric].
2599  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ 0 = #F›
2600    using "card-en"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "→E", OF "zero-card", THEN "∀E"(2)].
2601  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ #F = 0›
2602    by (simp add: "deduction-theorem" id_sym "≡I")
2603  finally show ?thesis.
2604qed

2606AOT_define Hereditary :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹Hereditary'(_,_')›)
2607  "hered:1": ‹Hereditary(F, R) ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & ∀x∀y([R]xy → ([F]x → [F]y))›

2609AOT_theorem "hered:2": ‹[λxy ∀F((∀z([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R)) → [F]y)]↓›
2610  by "cqt:2[lambda]"

2612AOT_define StrongAncestral :: ‹τ ⇒ Π› (‹_⇧*›)
2613  "ances-df": ‹R⇧* =⇩d⇩f [λxy ∀F((∀z([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R)) → [F]y)]›

2615AOT_theorem ances: ‹[R⇧*]xy ≡ ∀F((∀z([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R)) → [F]y)›
2616  apply (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "ances-df"])
2617   apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
2618  apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF "hered:2", unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified])
2619  by (simp add: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")

2621AOT_theorem "anc-her:1": ‹[R]xy → [R⇧*]xy›
2622proof (safe intro!: "→I" ances[THEN "≡E"(2)] GEN)
2623  fix F
2624  AOT_assume ‹∀z ([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F, R)›
2625  AOT_hence ‹[R]xy → [F]y› using "∀E"(2) "&E" by blast
2626  moreover AOT_assume ‹[R]xy›
2627  ultimately AOT_show ‹[F]y› using "→E" by blast
2628qed
2629
2630AOT_theorem "anc-her:2": ‹([R⇧*]xy & ∀z([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R)) → [F]y›
2631proof(rule "→I"; (frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))+)
2632  AOT_assume ‹[R⇧*]xy›
2633  AOT_hence ‹(∀z([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R)) → [F]y›
2634    using ances[THEN "≡E"(1)] "∀E"(2) by blast
2635  moreover AOT_assume ‹∀z([R]xz → [F]z)›
2636  moreover AOT_assume ‹Hereditary(F,R)›
2637  ultimately AOT_show ‹[F]y› using "→E" "&I" by blast
2638qed

2640AOT_theorem "anc-her:3": ‹([F]x & [R⇧*]xy & Hereditary(F, R)) → [F]y›
2641proof(rule "→I"; (frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))+)
2642  AOT_assume 1: ‹[F]x›
2643  AOT_assume 2: ‹Hereditary(F, R)›
2644  AOT_hence 3: ‹∀x ∀y ([R]xy → ([F]x → [F]y))› using "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
2645  AOT_have ‹∀z ([R]xz → [F]z)›
2646  proof (rule GEN; rule "→I")
2647    fix z
2648    AOT_assume ‹[R]xz›
2649    moreover AOT_have ‹[R]xz → ([F]x → [F]z)› using 3 "∀E"(2) by blast
2650    ultimately AOT_show ‹[F]z› using 1 "→E" by blast
2651  qed
2652  moreover AOT_assume ‹[R⇧*]xy›
2653  ultimately AOT_show ‹[F]y›
2654    by (auto intro!: 2 "anc-her:2"[THEN "→E"] "&I")
2655qed

2657AOT_theorem "anc-her:4": ‹([R]xy & [R⇧*]yz) → [R⇧*]xz›
2658proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
2659  AOT_assume 0: ‹[R⇧*]yz› and 1: ‹[R]xy›
2660  AOT_show ‹[R⇧*]xz›
2661  proof(safe intro!: ances[THEN "≡E"(2)] GEN "&I" "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
2662    fix F
2663    AOT_assume ‹∀z ([R]xz → [F]z)›
2664    AOT_hence 1: ‹[F]y› using 1 "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
2665    AOT_assume 2: ‹Hereditary(F,R)›
2666    AOT_show ‹[F]z›
2667      by (rule "anc-her:3"[THEN "→E"]; auto intro!: "&I" 1 2 0)
2668  qed
2669qed

2671AOT_theorem "anc-her:5": ‹[R⇧*]xy → ∃z [R]zy›
2672proof (rule "→I")
2673  AOT_have 0: ‹[λy ∃x [R]xy]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2674  AOT_assume 1: ‹[R⇧*]xy›
2675  AOT_have ‹[λy∃x [R]xy]y›
2676  proof(rule "anc-her:2"[unvarify F, OF 0, THEN "→E"];
2677        safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] 0)
2678    AOT_show ‹[R⇧*]xy› using 1.
2679  next
2680    fix z
2681    AOT_assume ‹[R]xz›
2682    AOT_hence ‹∃x [R]xz› by (rule "∃I")
2683    AOT_thus ‹[λy∃x [R]xy]z›
2684      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
2685  next
2686    fix x y
2687    AOT_assume ‹[R]xy›
2688    AOT_hence ‹∃x [R]xy› by (rule "∃I")
2689    AOT_thus ‹[λy ∃x [R]xy]y›
2690      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
2691  qed
2692  AOT_thus ‹∃z [R]zy›
2693    by (rule "β→C"(1))
2694qed

2696AOT_theorem "anc-her:6": ‹([R⇧*]xy & [R⇧*]yz) → [R⇧*]xz›
2697proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
2698  AOT_assume ‹[R⇧*]xy›
2699  AOT_hence θ: ‹∀z ([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R) → [F]y› for F
2700    using "∀E"(2)  ances[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2701  AOT_assume ‹[R⇧*]yz›
2702  AOT_hence ξ: ‹∀z ([R]yz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R) → [F]z› for F
2703    using "∀E"(2) ances[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2704  AOT_show ‹[R⇧*]xz›
2705  proof (rule ances[THEN "≡E"(2)]; safe intro!: GEN "→I")
2706    fix F
2707    AOT_assume ζ: ‹∀z ([R]xz → [F]z) & Hereditary(F,R)›
2708    AOT_show ‹[F]z›
2709    proof (rule ξ[THEN "→E", OF "&I"])
2710      AOT_show ‹Hereditary(F,R)› using ζ[THEN "&E"(2)].
2711    next
2712      AOT_show ‹∀z ([R]yz → [F]z)›
2713      proof(rule GEN; rule "→I")
2714        fix z
2715        AOT_assume ‹[R]yz›
2716        moreover AOT_have ‹[F]y› using θ[THEN "→E", OF ζ].
2717        ultimately AOT_show ‹[F]z›
2718          using ζ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2),
2719                  THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E"]
2720          by blast
2721      qed
2722    qed
2723  qed
2724qed

2729AOT_define RigidOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1'(_')›)
2730  "df-1-1:2": ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(R) ≡⇩d⇩f 1-1(R) & Rigid(R)›
2731
2732AOT_theorem "df-1-1:3": ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(R) → □1-1(R)›
2733proof(rule "→I")
2734  AOT_assume ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(R)›
2735  AOT_hence ‹1-1(R)› and RigidR: ‹Rigid(R)› using "df-1-1:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
2736  AOT_hence 1: ‹[R]xz & [R]yz → x = y› for x y z using "df-1-1:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E"(2) "∀E"(2) by blast
2737  AOT_have 1: ‹[R]xz & [R]yz → □x = y› for x y z
2738    by (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹□x = y›  ‹x = y›)
2739       (auto simp: 1 "id-nec:2" "≡I" "qml:2" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
2740  AOT_have ‹□∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([R]x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R]x⇩1...x⇩n)› using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF RigidR] "&E" by blast
2741  AOT_hence ‹∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n □([R]x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R]x⇩1...x⇩n)› using "CBF"[THEN "→E"] by fast
2742  AOT_hence ‹∀x⇩1∀x⇩2 □([R]x⇩1x⇩2 → □[R]x⇩1x⇩2)› using tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2743  AOT_hence ‹□([R]xy → □[R]xy)› for x y using "∀E"(2) by blast
2744  AOT_hence ‹□(([R]xz → □[R]xz) & ([R]yz → □[R]yz))› for x y z by (metis "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(3) "raa-cor:3")
2745  moreover AOT_have ‹□(([R]xz → □[R]xz) & ([R]yz → □[R]yz)) → □(([R]xz & [R]yz) → □([R]xz & [R]yz))› for x y z
2746    by (rule RM) (metis "→I" "KBasic:3" "&I" "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "≡E"(2) "vdash-properties:10")
2747  ultimately AOT_have 2: ‹□(([R]xz & [R]yz) → □([R]xz & [R]yz))› for x y z using "→E" by blast
2748  AOT_hence 3: ‹□([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y)› for x y z using "sc-eq-box-box:6"[THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF 2, OF 1] by blast
2749  AOT_hence 4: ‹□∀x∀y∀z([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y)›
2750    by (safe intro!: GEN BF[THEN "→E"] 3)
2751  AOT_show ‹□1-1(R)›
2752    apply (AOT_subst ‹1-1(R)› ‹∀x∀y∀z([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y)›)
2753    using "df-1-1:1"[THEN "≡Df", THEN "≡S"(1), OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]]
2754    using 4 by auto
2755qed

2757AOT_theorem "df-1-1:4": ‹∀R(Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(R) → □Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(R))›
2758proof(rule GEN;rule "→I")
2759AOT_modally_strict {
2760  fix R
2761      AOT_assume 0: ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(R)›
2762      AOT_hence 1: ‹R↓›
2763        by (meson "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) "df-1-1:1" "df-1-1:2")
2764      AOT_hence 2: ‹□R↓› using "exist-nec" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
2765      AOT_have 4: ‹□1-1(R)›
2766        using "df-1-1:3"[unvarify R, OF 1, THEN "→E", OF 0].
2767      AOT_have ‹Rigid(R)› using 0 "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "df-1-1:2"] "&E" by blast
2768      AOT_hence ‹□∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([R]x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R]x⇩1...x⇩n)› using  "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
2769      AOT_hence 5: ‹□□∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([R]x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R]x⇩1...x⇩n)› by (metis "S5Basic:6" "≡E"(1))
2770      AOT_have 6: ‹□Rigid(R)›
2771        apply (AOT_subst_using subst: "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡Df"])
2772        using 2 5 "KBasic:3" "≡S"(2) "≡E"(2) by blast
2773      AOT_show ‹□Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(R)›
2774        apply (AOT_subst_using subst: "df-1-1:2"[THEN "≡Df"])
2775        using 4 6 "KBasic:3" "≡S"(2) "≡E"(2) by blast
2776}
2777qed

2780AOT_define InDomainOf :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹InDomainOf'(_,_')›)
2781  "df-1-1:5": ‹InDomainOf(x, R) ≡⇩d⇩f ∃y [R]xy›
2782
2783AOT_register_rigid_restricted_type
2784  RigidOneToOneRelation: ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(Π)›
2785proof
2786  AOT_modally_strict {
2787    AOT_show ‹∃α Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(α)›
2788    proof (rule "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«(=⇩E)»›])
2789      AOT_show ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1((=⇩E))›
2790      proof (safe intro!: "df-1-1:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "df-1-1:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] GEN "→I" "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "=E[denotes]")
2791        fix x y z
2792        AOT_assume ‹x =⇩E z & y =⇩E z›
2793        AOT_thus ‹x = y›
2794          by (metis "rule=E" "&E"(1) "Conjunction Simplification"(2) "=E-simple:2" id_sym "vdash-properties:10")
2795      next
2796        AOT_have ‹∀x∀y □(x =⇩E y → □x =⇩E y)›
2797        proof(rule GEN; rule GEN)
2798          AOT_show ‹□(x =⇩E y → □x =⇩E y)› for x y
2799            by (meson RN "deduction-theorem" "id-nec3:1" "≡E"(1))
2800        qed
2801        AOT_hence ‹∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n □([(=⇩E)]x⇩1...x⇩n → □[(=⇩E)]x⇩1...x⇩n)›
2802          by (rule tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
2803        AOT_thus ‹□∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([(=⇩E)]x⇩1...x⇩n → □[(=⇩E)]x⇩1...x⇩n)›
2804          using BF[THEN "→E"] by fast
2805      qed
2806    qed(fact "=E[denotes]")
2807  }
2808next
2809  AOT_modally_strict {
2810    AOT_show ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(Π) → Π↓› for Π
2811    proof(rule "→I")
2812      AOT_assume ‹Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(Π)›
2813      AOT_hence ‹1-1(Π)› using "df-1-1:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
2814      AOT_thus ‹Π↓› using "df-1-1:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
2815    qed
2816  } note 1 = this
2817  AOT_modally_strict {
2818    AOT_show ‹□(Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(Π) → □Rigid⇩1⇩-⇩1(Π))› for Π
2819      using "df-1-1:4"[THEN "∀E"(1), OF 1[THEN "→E"], THEN "→E"] "→I" RN by blast
2820  }
2821qed

2823  RigidOneToOneRelation: ℛ 𝒮

2825AOT_define IdentityRestrictedToDomain :: ‹τ ⇒ Π› (‹'(=⇩_')›)
2826  "id-d-R": ‹(=⇩ℛ) =⇩d⇩f [λxy ∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)]›
2827
2828syntax "_AOT_id_d_R_infix" :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› ("(_ =⇩_/ _)" [50, 51, 51] 50)
2829translations
2830  "_AOT_id_d_R_infix κ Π κ'" == "CONST AOT_exe (CONST IdentityRestrictedToDomain Π) (κ,κ')"
2831
2832AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:1": ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ ∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)›
2833proof -
2834  AOT_have 0: ‹[λxy ∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2835  show ?thesis
2836    apply (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "id-d-R"])
2837    apply (fact 0)
2838    apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF 0, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified])
2839    by (simp add: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
2840qed

2842AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:2": ‹x =⇩ℛ y → (InDomainOf(x, ℛ) & InDomainOf(y, ℛ))›
2843proof(rule "→I")
2844  AOT_assume ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
2845  AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)› using "id-R-thm:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by simp
2846  then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2847  AOT_show ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ) & InDomainOf(y, ℛ)›
2848  proof (safe intro!: "&I" "df-1-1:5"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
2849    AOT_show ‹∃y [ℛ]xy› using z_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "∃I" by fast
2850  next
2851    AOT_show ‹∃z [ℛ]yz› using z_prop[THEN "&E"(2)] "∃I" by fast
2852  qed
2853qed
2854
2855AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:3": ‹x =⇩ℛ y → x = y›
2856proof(rule "→I")
2857  AOT_assume ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
2858  AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)› using "id-R-thm:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by simp
2859  then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2860  AOT_thus ‹x = y›
2861    using "df-1-1:3"[THEN "→E", OF RigidOneToOneRelation.ψ, THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"],
2862                     THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "df-1-1:1"], THEN "&E"(2),THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2),
2863                     THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
2864     by blast
2865qed
2866
2867AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:4": ‹(InDomainOf(x, ℛ) ∨ InDomainOf(y, ℛ)) → (x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y)›
2868proof (rule "→I")
2869  AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ) ∨ InDomainOf(y, ℛ)›
2870  moreover {
2871    AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ)›
2872    AOT_hence ‹∃z [ℛ]xz› by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "df-1-1:5")
2873    then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2874    AOT_have ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
2875    proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "id-R-thm:3"[THEN "→E"])
2876      AOT_assume ‹x = y›
2877      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]yz› using z_prop "rule=E" by fast
2878      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz› using z_prop "&I" by blast
2879      AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)› by (rule "∃I")
2880      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
2881        using "id-R-thm:1" "≡E"(2) by blast
2882    qed
2883  }
2884  moreover {
2885    AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(y, ℛ)›
2886    AOT_hence ‹∃z [ℛ]yz› by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "df-1-1:5")
2887    then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]yz› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2888    AOT_have ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
2889    proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "id-R-thm:3"[THEN "→E"])
2890      AOT_assume ‹x = y›
2891      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz› using z_prop "rule=E" id_sym by fast
2892      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz› using z_prop "&I" by blast
2893      AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)› by (rule "∃I")
2894      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
2895        using "id-R-thm:1" "≡E"(2) by blast
2896    qed
2897  }
2898  ultimately AOT_show ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
2899    by (metis "∨E"(2) "raa-cor:1")
2900qed
2901
2902AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:5": ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ) → x =⇩ℛ x›
2903proof (rule "→I")
2904  AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ)›
2905  AOT_hence ‹∃z [ℛ]xz› by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "df-1-1:5")
2906  then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2907  AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]xz› using "&I" by blast
2908  AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]xz)› using "∃I" by fast
2909  AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ x›
2910    using "id-R-thm:1" "≡E"(2) by blast
2911qed

2913AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:6": ‹x =⇩ℛ y → y =⇩ℛ x›
2914proof(rule "→I")
2915  AOT_assume 0: ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
2916  AOT_hence 1: ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ) & InDomainOf(y,ℛ)› using "id-R-thm:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
2917  AOT_hence ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
2918    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
2919  AOT_hence ‹x = y› using 0 by (metis "≡E"(1))
2920  AOT_hence ‹y = x› using id_sym by blast
2921  moreover AOT_have ‹y =⇩ℛ x ≡ y = x›
2922    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(2)] 1 "&E" by blast
2923  ultimately AOT_show ‹y =⇩ℛ x›
2924    by (metis "≡E"(2))
2925qed

2927AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:7": ‹x =⇩ℛ y & y =⇩ℛ z → x =⇩ℛ z›
2928proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
2929  AOT_assume 0: ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
2930  AOT_hence 1: ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ) & InDomainOf(y,ℛ)› using "id-R-thm:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
2931  AOT_hence ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
2932    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
2933  AOT_hence x_eq_y: ‹x = y› using 0 by (metis "≡E"(1))
2934  AOT_assume 2: ‹y =⇩ℛ z›
2935  AOT_hence 3: ‹InDomainOf(y,ℛ) & InDomainOf(z,ℛ)› using "id-R-thm:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
2936  AOT_hence ‹y =⇩ℛ z ≡ y = z›
2937    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
2938  AOT_hence ‹y = z› using 2 by (metis "≡E"(1))
2939  AOT_hence x_eq_z: ‹x = z› using x_eq_y id_trans by blast
2940  AOT_have ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ) & InDomainOf(z,ℛ)› using 1 3 "&I" "&E" by meson
2941  AOT_hence ‹x =⇩ℛ z ≡ x = z›
2942    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
2943  AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ z› using x_eq_z "≡E"(2) by blast
2944qed

2946AOT_define WeakAncestral :: ‹Π ⇒ Π› (‹_⇧+›)
2947  "w-ances-df": ‹[ℛ]⇧+ =⇩d⇩f [λxy [ℛ]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y]›
2948
2949AOT_theorem "w-ances-df[den1]": ‹[λxy [Π]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩Π y]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2950AOT_theorem "w-ances-df[den2]": ‹[Π]⇧+↓› using "w-ances-df[den1]" "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "w-ances-df"] by blast

2952AOT_theorem "w-ances": ‹[ℛ]⇧+xy ≡ ([ℛ]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y)›
2953proof -
2954  AOT_have 0: ‹[λxy [ℛ⇧*]xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2955  (* TODO: try to prevent 1 and 2 from being needed *)
2956  AOT_have 1: ‹«(AOT_term_of_var x,AOT_term_of_var y)»↓›
2957    by (simp add: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
2958  have 2: ‹«[λμ⇩1...μ⇩n [ℛ⇧*]μ⇩1...μ⇩n ∨ [(=⇩ℛ)]μ⇩1...μ⇩n]xy» = «[λxy [ℛ⇧*]xy ∨ [(=⇩ℛ)]xy]xy»›
2959    by (simp add: cond_case_prod_eta)
2960  show ?thesis
2961    apply (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "w-ances-df"])
2962     apply (fact "w-ances-df[den1]")
2963    using "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF 0, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF 1] 2 by simp
2964qed

3203proof (rule "→I")

3205  AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y› by (metis "≡E"(1) "w-ances")
3206  moreover {
3207    AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy›
3208    AOT_hence ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ)› using "1-1-R:4" "→E" by blast
3209  }
3210  moreover {
3211    AOT_assume ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3212    AOT_hence ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ)› by (metis "Conjunction Simplification"(1) "id-R-thm:2" "vdash-properties:6")
3213  }
3214  ultimately AOT_show ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ)› by (metis "∨E"(3) "reductio-aa:1")
3215qed

3217AOT_theorem "pre-ind": ‹([F]z & ∀x∀y(([ℛ]⇧+zx & [ℛ]⇧+zy) → ([ℛ]xy → ([F]x → [F]y)))) → ∀x ([ℛ]⇧+zx → [F]x)›
3218proof(safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
3219  AOT_have den: ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3220  fix x
3221  AOT_assume θ: ‹[F]z & ∀x∀y(([ℛ]⇧+zx & [ℛ]⇧+zy) → ([ℛ]xy → ([F]x → [F]y)))›
3222  AOT_assume 0: ‹[ℛ]⇧+zx›
3223
3224  AOT_have ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]x›
3225  proof (rule "w-ances-her:2"[unvarify F, OF den, THEN "→E"]; safe intro!: "&I")
3226    AOT_show ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]z›
3227    proof (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I")
3228      AOT_show ‹[F]z› using θ "&E" by blast
3229    next
3230      AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧+zz›
3231        by (rule "w-ances"[THEN "≡E"(2), OF "∨I"(2)])
3232           (meson "0" "id-R-thm:5" "1-1-R:5" "→E")
3233    qed
3234  next
3235    AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧+zx› by (fact 0)
3236  next
3237    AOT_show ‹Hereditary([λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy],ℛ)›
3238    proof (safe intro!: "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" GEN "→I")
3239      fix x' y
3240      AOT_assume 1: ‹[ℛ]x'y›
3241      AOT_assume ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]x'›
3242      AOT_hence 2: ‹[F]x' & [ℛ]⇧+zx'› by (rule "β→C"(1))
3243      AOT_have ‹[ℛ]⇧*zy› using 1 2[THEN "&E"(2)]
3244        by (metis Adjunction "modus-tollens:1" "reductio-aa:1" "w-ances-her:3")
3245      AOT_hence 3: ‹[ℛ]⇧+zy› by (metis "∨I"(1) "≡E"(2) "w-ances")
3246      AOT_show ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]y›
3247      proof (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" 3)
3248        AOT_show ‹[F]y›
3249        proof (rule θ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E", THEN "→E"])
3250          AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧+zx' & [ℛ]⇧+zy›
3251            using 2 3 "&E" "&I" by blast
3252        next
3253          AOT_show ‹[ℛ]x'y› by (fact 1)
3254        next
3255          AOT_show ‹[F]x'› using 2 "&E" by blast
3256        qed
3257      qed
3258    qed
3259  qed
3260  AOT_thus ‹[F]x› using "β→C"(1) "&E"(1) by fast
3261qed

3263AOT_theorem denotes_all: ‹[λx ∀G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]↓›
3264proof -
3265  AOT_modally_strict {
3266    fix x y
3267    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3268    AOT_hence nec_indist: ‹□∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)› 
3269      using "ind-nec" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
3270    AOT_hence indist_nec: ‹∀F □([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3271      using "CBF" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
3272    AOT_assume 0: ‹∀G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])›
3273    AOT_have ‹x[F]›
3274      by (safe intro!: 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] GEN "→I" RN "≡I")
3275    AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› by (metis "encoders-are-abstract" "existential:2[const_var]" "→E")
3276    AOT_hence Ay: ‹A!y› using indist "∀E"(1) "≡E"(1) "oa-exist:2" by blast
3277    AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])›
3278        using indistinguishable_ord_enc_all[axiom_inst, THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "&I", OF "&I",
3279            OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst], OF Ax, OF Ay, OF indist_nec, THEN "≡E"(1), OF 0].
3280  } note 0 = this
3281  AOT_modally_strict {
3282    fix x y
3283    AOT_assume ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3284    moreover AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]y ≡ [F]x)›
3285      by (metis calculation "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(2))
3286    ultimately AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G]) ≡ ∀G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])›
3287      using 0 "≡I" "→I" by auto
3288  } note 1 = this
3289  AOT_show ‹[λx ∀G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]↓›
3290    by (safe intro!: RN GEN "→I" 1 "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
3291qed

3293AOT_theorem denotes_ex: ‹[λx ∃G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) & x[G])]↓›
3294proof -
3295  AOT_modally_strict {
3296    fix x y
3297    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3298    AOT_hence nec_indist: ‹□∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)› 
3299      using "ind-nec" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
3300    AOT_hence indist_nec: ‹∀F □([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3301      using "CBF" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
3302    AOT_assume 0: ‹∃G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) & x[G])›
3303    then AOT_obtain G where ‹∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) & x[G]› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3304    AOT_hence ‹x[G]› using "&E" by blast
3305    AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› by (metis "encoders-are-abstract" "existential:2[const_var]" "→E")
3306    AOT_hence Ay: ‹A!y› using indist "∀E"(1) "≡E"(1) "oa-exist:2" by blast
3307    AOT_have ‹∃G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) & y[G])›
3308      using indistinguishable_ord_enc_ex[axiom_inst, THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "&I", OF "&I", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst], OF Ax,
3309          OF Ay, OF indist_nec, THEN "≡E"(1), OF 0].
3310  } note 0 = this
3311  AOT_modally_strict {
3312    fix x y
3313    AOT_assume ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3314    moreover AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]y ≡ [F]x)›
3315      by (metis calculation "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(2))
3316    ultimately AOT_have ‹∃G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) & x[G]) ≡ ∃G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) & y[G])›
3317      using 0 "≡I" "→I" by auto
3318  } note 1 = this
3319  AOT_show ‹[λx ∃G (∀u □([G]u ≡ [F]u) & x[G])]↓›
3320    by (safe intro!: RN GEN "→I" 1 "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
3321qed

3323AOT_theorem numbers_prop_den: ‹[λx Numbers(x, F)]↓›
3324proof - 
3325  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3326  AOT_have act_beta: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u ≡ ❙𝒜[F]u› for F u
3327    by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
3328  AOT_modally_strict {
3329    fix v and x y
3330    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3331    AOT_hence ‹□∀F([F]x ≡ [F]y)› using "ind-nec" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
3332    AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, F) → Numbers(y, F)›
3333    proof(safe intro!: "→I")
3334      AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, F)›
3335
3336      AOT_hence x_prop: ‹[A!]x & ∀G (x[G] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[G]z] ≈⇩E F)›
3337        using "numbers[den]"[THEN "→E", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst], THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
3338      AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› and x_enc_cond: ‹x[G] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[G]z] ≈⇩E F› for G
3339        using "&E" "∀E" by blast+
3340      AOT_have Ay: ‹A!y›
3341        using indist Ax "≡E"(1) "oa-exist:2" "rule-ui:1" by blast
3342
3343      {
3344        fix G
3345        AOT_assume G_act_equinum_F: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[G]z] ≈⇩E F›
3346        AOT_hence ‹x[G]› by (metis "≡E"(2) x_enc_cond)
3347        {
3348          fix H
3349          AOT_assume ‹∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u)›
3350          AOT_hence ‹□∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u)›
3351            by (metis "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]" "→E")
3352          AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u)› by (metis "nec-imp-act" "vdash-properties:6")
3353          AOT_hence 0: ‹∀u ❙𝒜([H]u ≡ [G]u)›  by (metis "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[3]" "vdash-properties:10")
3354          {
3355            fix u
3356            AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([H]u ≡ [G]u)› using 0 "Ordinary.∀E" by fast
3357            AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[H]u ≡ ❙𝒜[G]u› by (metis "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(1))
3358            AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]u›
3359              using act_beta by (metis "deduction-theorem" "≡I" "≡E"(1) "≡E"(2))
3360          } note 1 = this
3361          AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]›
3362            by (rule eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
3363               (auto intro!: "&I" act_den Ordinary.GEN "→I" 1)
3364          AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]›
3365            using "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify F G, OF act_den, OF act_den, THEN "→E"] by blast
3366          AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F›
3367            by (metis G_act_equinum_F "eq-part:3[terms]")
3368          AOT_hence ‹x[H]› by (metis "≡E"(2) x_enc_cond)
3369        }
3370        AOT_hence ‹(∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) → x[H])› for H by (rule "→I")
3371        AOT_hence ‹∀H(∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) → x[H])› by (rule GEN)
3372        AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀H(∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) → x[H])]x›
3373          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) denotes_all simp: "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
3374        AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀H(∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) → x[H])]y›
3375          using indist[THEN "∀E"(1), OF denotes_all, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
3376        AOT_hence ‹∀H(∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) → y[H])›
3377          by (rule "β→C"(1))
3378        moreover AOT_have ‹∀u □([G]u ≡ [G]u)›
3379          by (safe intro!: GEN "→I" RN "≡I")
3380        ultimately AOT_have ‹y[G]› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
3381      }
3382      moreover {
3383        fix G
3384        AOT_assume yG: ‹y[G]›
3385        AOT_hence ‹∃H (∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) & y[H])›
3386          by (safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=‹G›] yG "&I" "→I" GEN RN "≡I")
3387        AOT_hence ‹[λy ∃H (∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) & y[H])]y›
3388          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) denotes_ex intro: "cqt:2")
3389        AOT_hence ‹[λy ∃H (∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) & y[H])]x›
3390          using indist[THEN "∀E"(1), OF denotes_ex, THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
3391        AOT_hence ‹∃H (∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u) & x[H])›
3392          by (rule "β→C"(1))
3393        then AOT_obtain H where H_eq_G: ‹∀u □([H]u ≡ [G]u)› and x_enc_H: ‹x[H]› using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3394        AOT_have actH_equinum_F: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F›
3395          using "≡E"(1) x_enc_H x_enc_cond by blast
3396        AOT_have ‹□∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u)›
3397          by (metis H_eq_G "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]" "vdash-properties:10")
3398        AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u)›
3399          by (metis "nec-imp-act" "vdash-properties:6")
3400        AOT_hence ‹∀u ❙𝒜([H]u ≡ [G]u)›
3401          by (metis "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[3]" "vdash-properties:10")
3402        AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜([H]u ≡ [G]u)› if ‹O!u› for u using that "∀E"(2) "→E" by fast
3403        AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[H]u ≡ ❙𝒜[G]u› if ‹O!u› for u
3404          by (metis "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(1) that)
3405        AOT_hence 0: ‹[λx ❙𝒜[H]x]u ≡ [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]u› if ‹O!u› for u
3406          by (metis act_beta "deduction-theorem" "≡I" "≡E"(1) "≡E"(2) that)
3407        AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]›
3408          apply (rule "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify F G, OF act_den, OF act_den, THEN "→E"])
3409          apply (rule eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
3410          by (safe intro!: "&I" act_den Ordinary.GEN Ordinary.ψ "→I" 0)
3411        AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[G]z] ≈⇩E F›
3412          using actH_equinum_F by (metis "eq-part:2[terms]" "eq-part:3[terms]" "vdash-properties:10")
3413      }
3414      ultimately AOT_have ‹y[G] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[G]z] ≈⇩E F› for G
3415        by (metis "deduction-theorem" "≡I")
3416      AOT_hence 0: ‹∀G (y[G] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[G]z] ≈⇩E F)›
3417        by (rule GEN)
3418      AOT_show ‹Numbers(y, F)›
3419        by (safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" Ay "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] 0)
3420    qed
3421  } note 0 = this
3422  AOT_modally_strict {
3423    fix v and x y
3424    AOT_assume ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
3425    moreover AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]y ≡ [F]x)›
3426      by (metis calculation "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(1))
3427    ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, F) ≡ Numbers(y, F)›
3428      using 0 "≡I" by simp
3429  } note 0 = this
3430  AOT_show ‹[λx Numbers(x,F)]↓›
3431    apply (rule "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)]; rule RN)
3432    apply (rule GEN)
3433    apply (rule GEN)
3434    using 0 "→I" by simp
3435qed

3437AOT_theorem pred: ‹[λxy ∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))]↓›
3438proof -
3439  AOT_have prod_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ «(AOT_term_of_var x⇩1,AOT_term_of_var x⇩2)»↓› for x⇩1 x⇩2 :: ‹κ AOT_var›
3440    by (simp add: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
3441  AOT_have proj1_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λxy [F]x]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3442  AOT_have proj2_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λxy [F]y]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3443  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3444  AOT_have act_beta: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u ≡ ❙𝒜[F]u› for F u
3445    by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
3446  AOT_modally_strict {
3447    fix x⇩1 x⇩2 y⇩1 y⇩2
3448    AOT_assume 0: ‹∀F ([F]x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩1y⇩2)›
3449    AOT_have ‹[λxy [F]x]x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [λxy [F]x]y⇩1y⇩2› for F
3450      by (rule 0[THEN "∀E"(1)]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
3451    AOT_have ‹ ❙⊢⇩□ ψ{[λμ⇩1...μ⇩n φ{μ⇩1...μ⇩n}]} ≡ ψ{[λxy φ{«(x,y)»}]}› for φ ψ
3452      by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a")
3453    AOT_have xy1_eq: ‹([F]x⇩1 ≡ [F]y⇩1)› for F
3454      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]x⇩1› ‹[λxy [F]x]x⇩1x⇩2›)
3455       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj1_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3456      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]y⇩1› ‹[λxy [F]x]y⇩1y⇩2›)
3457       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj1_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3458      using "0" proj1_den "rule-ui:1" by blast
3459    AOT_hence ‹∀F([F]x⇩1 ≡ [F]y⇩1)› by (rule GEN)
3460    AOT_have xy2_eq: ‹([F]x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩2)› for F
3461      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]x⇩2› ‹[λxy [F]y]x⇩1x⇩2›)
3462       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj2_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3463      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]y⇩2› ‹[λxy [F]y]y⇩1y⇩2›)
3464       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj2_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3465      using "0" proj2_den "rule-ui:1" by blast
3466    AOT_hence ‹∀F([F]x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩2)› by (rule GEN)
3467
3468    AOT_have ‹(∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))) →
3469              (∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y⇩2,F) & Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)))›
3470    proof (rule "→I")
3471      AOT_assume ‹∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3472      then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3473      then AOT_obtain u where ‹[F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)› using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
3474      AOT_hence Fu: ‹[F]u›
3475            and numbers_x2_F: ‹Numbers(x⇩2,F)›
3476            and numbers_x1_F_minus_u: ‹Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)›
3477        using "&E" by blast+
3478
3479      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,F)]x⇩2›
3480        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) numbers_prop_den intro: "cqt:2")
3481      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,F)]y⇩2›
3482        using xy2_eq[unvarify F, OF numbers_prop_den, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
3483      AOT_hence numbers_y2_F: ‹Numbers(y⇩2,F)›
3484        by (rule "β→C"(1))
3485      AOT_have ‹[F]⇧-⇧u↓›
3486        using "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) "&E"(2) numbers numbers_x1_F_minus_u by blast
3487      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u)]x⇩1›
3488        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) numbers_prop_den[unvarify F] intro: "cqt:2" simp: numbers_x1_F_minus_u)
3489      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u)]y⇩1›
3490        using xy1_eq[unvarify F, OF numbers_prop_den[unvarify F, OF "F-u[den]"], THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
3491      AOT_hence numbers_y_1_F_minus_u: ‹Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)›
3492        by (rule "β→C"(1))
3493
3494      AOT_show ‹∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y⇩2,F) & Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3495        by (safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=F] "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u] "&I" Fu numbers_y2_F numbers_y_1_F_minus_u)
3496    qed
3497  } note 0 = this
3498  AOT_modally_strict {
3499    fix x⇩1 x⇩2 y⇩1 y⇩2
3500    AOT_assume ‹∀F ([F]x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩1y⇩2)›
3501    moreover AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]y⇩1y⇩2 ≡ [F]x⇩1x⇩2)›
3502      using calculation "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(1) by fastforce
3503    ultimately AOT_have ‹∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)) ≡
3504                         ∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y⇩2,F) & Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3505      using 0 "≡I" "→E" by auto
3506  } note 0 = this
3507  AOT_show ‹[λxy ∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))]↓›
3508    apply (rule "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)]; rule RN)
3509    apply (rule tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
3510    apply (rule GEN)
3511    apply (rule GEN)
3512    apply (rule tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
3513    apply (rule GEN)
3514    apply (rule GEN)
3515    using 0 "→I" by simp
3516qed

3535AOT_theorem "pred-1-1:1": ‹[𝒫]xy → □[𝒫]xy›
3536proof(rule "→I")
3537  AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xy›
3538  AOT_hence ‹∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3539    using "≡E"(1) "pred-thm:3" by fast
3540  then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3541    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3542  then AOT_obtain u where props: ‹[F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u)›
3543    using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
3544  AOT_obtain G where Ridigifies_G_F: ‹Rigidifies(G, F)›
3545    by (metis "instantiation" "rigid-der:3")
3546  AOT_hence ξ: ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x)› and ζ: ‹∀x([G]x ≡ [F]x)›
3547    using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1), THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "df-rigid-rel:1"], THEN "&E"(2)]
3548          "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast+
3549
3550  AOT_have rigid_num_nec: ‹Numbers(x,F) & Rigidifies(G,F) → □Numbers(x,G)› for x G F
3551  proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
3552    fix G F x
3553    AOT_assume Numbers_xF: ‹Numbers(x,F)›
3554    AOT_assume ‹Rigidifies(G,F)›
3555    AOT_hence ξ: ‹Rigid(G)› and ζ: ‹∀x([G]x ≡ [F]x)›
3556      using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
3557    AOT_thus ‹□Numbers(x,G)›
3558    proof (safe intro!:
3559          "num-cont:2"[THEN "→E", OF ξ, THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"], THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
3560          "num-tran:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1), rotated, OF Numbers_xF]
3561          eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
3562            "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I")
3563      AOT_show ‹[F]u ≡ [G]u› for u
3564        using ζ[THEN "∀E"(2)] by (metis "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a") 
3565    qed
3566  qed
3567  AOT_have ‹□Numbers(y,G)›
3568    using rigid_num_nec[THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF props[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)], OF Ridigifies_G_F].
3569  moreover {
3570    AOT_have ‹Rigidifies([G]⇧-⇧u, [F]⇧-⇧u)›
3571    proof (safe intro!: "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "F-u[den]" GEN "≡I" "→I")
3572      AOT_have ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x) → □∀x([[G]⇧-⇧u]x → □[[G]⇧-⇧u]x)›
3573      proof (rule RM; safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
3574        AOT_modally_strict {
3575          fix x
3576          AOT_assume 0: ‹∀x([G]x → □[G]x)›
3577          AOT_assume 1: ‹[[G]⇧-⇧u]x›
3578          AOT_have ‹[λx [G]x & x ≠⇩E u]x›
3579            apply (rule "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
3580             apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
3581            by (fact 1)
3582          AOT_hence ‹[G]x & x ≠⇩E u›
3583            by (rule "β→C"(1))
3584          AOT_hence 2: ‹□[G]x› and 3: ‹□x ≠⇩E u›
3585            using "&E" 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] "id-nec4:1" "≡E"(1) by blast+
3586          AOT_show ‹□[[G]⇧-⇧u]x›
3587            apply (AOT_subst ‹[[G]⇧-⇧u]x› ‹[G]x & x ≠⇩E u›)
3588             apply (rule "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
3589              apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
3590             apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
3591            apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
3592            using 2 3 "KBasic:3" "≡S"(2) "≡E"(2) by blast
3593        }
3594      qed
3595      AOT_thus ‹□∀x([[G]⇧-⇧u]x → □[[G]⇧-⇧u]x)› using ξ "→E" by blast
3596    next
3597      fix x
3598      AOT_assume ‹[[G]⇧-⇧u]x›
3599      AOT_hence ‹[λx [G]x & x ≠⇩E u]x›
3600        by (auto intro: "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified] intro!: "cqt:2")
3601      AOT_hence ‹[G]x & x ≠⇩E u›
3602        by (rule "β→C"(1))
3603      AOT_hence ‹[F]x & x ≠⇩E u›
3604        using ζ "&I" "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "≡E"(1) "rule-ui:3" by blast
3605      AOT_hence ‹[λx [F]x & x ≠⇩E u]x›
3606        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
3607      AOT_thus ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]x›
3608        by (auto intro: "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified] intro!: "cqt:2")
3609    next
3610      fix x
3611      AOT_assume ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]x›
3612      AOT_hence ‹[λx [F]x & x ≠⇩E u]x›
3613        by (auto intro: "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified] intro!: "cqt:2")
3614      AOT_hence ‹[F]x & x ≠⇩E u›
3615        by (rule "β→C"(1))
3616      AOT_hence ‹[G]x & x ≠⇩E u›
3617        using ζ "&I" "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "≡E"(2) "rule-ui:3" by blast
3618      AOT_hence ‹[λx [G]x & x ≠⇩E u]x›
3619        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
3620      AOT_thus ‹[[G]⇧-⇧u]x›
3621        by (auto intro: "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified] intro!: "cqt:2")
3622    qed
3623    AOT_hence ‹□Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧u)›
3624      using rigid_num_nec[unvarify F G, OF "F-u[den]", OF "F-u[den]", THEN "→E", OF "&I",
3625              OF props[THEN "&E"(2)]] by blast
3626  }
3627  moreover AOT_have ‹□[G]u›
3628    using props[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1), THEN ζ[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(2)]]
3629          ξ[THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"], THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
3630  ultimately AOT_have ‹□([G]u & Numbers(y,G) & Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧u))›
3631    by (metis "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(2))
3632  AOT_hence ‹∃u (□([G]u & Numbers(y,G) & Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧u)))›
3633    by (rule "Ordinary.∃I")
3634  AOT_hence ‹□∃u ([G]u & Numbers(y,G) & Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧u))›
3635    using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[Buridan]" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
3636  AOT_hence ‹∃F □∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3637    by (rule "∃I")
3638  AOT_hence 0: ‹□∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3639    using Buridan "vdash-properties:10" by fast
3640  AOT_show ‹□[𝒫]xy›
3641    by (AOT_subst ‹[𝒫]xy› ‹∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›; simp add: "pred-thm:3" 0)
3642qed

3664  next

3670      using u_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
3671      using v_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
3672      using eqP'[THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "&I"]
3673      by blast
3674  qed
3675qed

3763AOT_theorem "assume1:5": ‹[𝒫]⇧+xy ≡ [𝒫]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩𝒫 y›
3764proof -
3765  AOT_have 0: ‹[λxy [𝒫]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩𝒫 y]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3766  AOT_have prod_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ «(AOT_term_of_var x⇩1,AOT_term_of_var x⇩2)»↓› for x⇩1 x⇩2 :: ‹κ AOT_var›
3767    by (simp add: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
3768  show ?thesis
3769    apply (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF "assume1:3"[symmetric]])
3770    using "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF 0, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n, OF prod_den, simplified, of x y]
3771    by (simp add: cond_case_prod_eta) (* TODO: try to avoid this *)
3772qed

3786AOT_theorem "0-n": ‹[ℕ]0›
3787proof (safe intro!: "nnumber:3"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(2)]
3788    "assume1:5"[unvarify x y, OF "zero:2", OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(2)]
3789    "∨I"(2) "assume1:2"[unvarify x y, OF "zero:2", OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(2)])
3790  fix u
3791  AOT_have den: ‹[λx O!x & x =⇩E u]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3792  AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹Numbers(a, [λx O!x & x =⇩E u])›
3793    using "num:1"[unvarify G, OF den] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3794  AOT_have ‹[𝒫]0a›
3795  proof (safe intro!: "pred-thm:3"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(2)]
3796                      "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«[λx O!x & x =⇩E u]»›] "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u] "&I" den
3797                      "0F:1"[unvarify F, OF "F-u[den]", unvarify F, OF den, THEN "≡E"(1)])
3798    AOT_show ‹[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]u›
3799      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E"] Ordinary.ψ)
3800  next
3801    AOT_show ‹Numbers(a,[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u])› using a_prop.
3802  next
3803    AOT_show ‹¬∃v [[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]⇧-⇧u]v›
3804    proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
3805      AOT_assume ‹∃v [[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]⇧-⇧u]v›
3806      then AOT_obtain v where ‹[[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]⇧-⇧u]v› using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
3807      AOT_hence ‹[λz [λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]z & z ≠⇩E u]v›
3808        apply (rule "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified, rotated])
3809        by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3810      AOT_hence ‹[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]v & v ≠⇩E u›
3811        by (rule "β→C"(1))
3812      AOT_hence ‹v =⇩E u› and ‹v ≠⇩E u› using "β→C"(1) "&E" by blast+
3813      AOT_hence ‹v =⇩E u & ¬(v =⇩E u)› by (metis "≡E"(4) "reductio-aa:1" "thm-neg=E")
3814      AOT_thus ‹p & ¬p› for p  by (metis "raa-cor:1")
3815    qed
3816  qed
3817  AOT_thus ‹∃z ([𝒫]0z & [𝒫]0z)›
3818    by (safe intro!: "&I" "∃I"(2)[where β=a])
3819qed

3821AOT_theorem "mod-col-num:1": ‹[ℕ]x → □[ℕ]x›
3822proof(rule "→I")
3823  AOT_have nec0N: ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]0›
3824    by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" simp: "zero:2" RN "0-n")
3825  AOT_have 1: ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]0 & ∀x∀y ([[𝒫]⇧+]0x & [[𝒫]⇧+]0y → ([𝒫]xy → ([λx □[ℕ]x]x → [λx □[ℕ]x]y))) → ∀x ([[𝒫]⇧+]0x → [λx □[ℕ]x]x)›
3826    by (auto intro!: "cqt:2" intro: "pre-ind"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β, OF "pred-thm:2", THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", unvarify z, OF "zero:2", unvarify F])
3827  AOT_have ‹∀x ([[𝒫]⇧+]0x → [λx □[ℕ]x]x)›
3828  proof (rule 1[THEN "→E"]; safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" nec0N; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
3829    fix x y
3830    AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xy›
3831    AOT_hence 0: ‹□[𝒫]xy› by (metis "pred-1-1:1" "vdash-properties:10")
3832    AOT_assume ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]x›
3833    AOT_hence ‹□[ℕ]x›
3834      by (rule "β→C"(1))
3835    AOT_hence ‹□([𝒫]xy & [ℕ]x)›
3836      by (metis "0" "KBasic:3" Adjunction "≡E"(2) "vdash-properties:10")
3837    moreover AOT_have ‹□([𝒫]xy & [ℕ]x) → □[ℕ]y›
3838    proof (rule RM; rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
3839      AOT_modally_strict {
3840        AOT_assume 0: ‹[𝒫]xy›
3841        AOT_assume ‹[ℕ]x›
3842        AOT_hence 1: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0x› by (metis "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3")
3843        AOT_show ‹[ℕ]y›
3844          apply (rule "nnumber:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
3845          apply (rule "assume1:5"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(2)])
3846          apply (rule "∨I"(1))
3847          apply (rule "w-ances-her:3"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β, OF "pred-thm:2", THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "→E"])
3848          apply (rule "&I")
3849           apply (fact 1)
3850          by (fact 0)
3851      }
3852    qed
3853    ultimately AOT_have ‹□[ℕ]y› by (metis "vdash-properties:10") 
3854    AOT_thus ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]y›
3855      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
3856  qed
3857  AOT_hence 0: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0x → [λx □[ℕ]x]x›
3858    using "∀E"(2) by blast
3859  AOT_assume ‹[ℕ]x›
3860  AOT_hence ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0x› by (metis "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3")
3861  AOT_hence ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]x› using 0[THEN "→E"] by blast
3862  AOT_thus ‹□[ℕ]x›
3863    by (rule "β→C"(1))
3864qed

3910AOT_theorem induction: ‹∀F([F]0 & ∀n∀m([𝒫]nm → ([F]n → [F]m)) → ∀n[F]n)›
3911proof (safe intro!: GEN[where 'a=‹<κ>›] Number.GEN "&I" "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
3912  fix F n
3913  AOT_assume F0: ‹[F]0›
3914  AOT_assume 0: ‹∀n∀m([𝒫]nm → ([F]n → [F]m))›
3915  {
3916    fix x y
3917    AOT_assume ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0x & [[𝒫]⇧+]0y›
3918    AOT_hence ‹[ℕ]x› and ‹[ℕ]y›
3919      using "&E" "≡E"(2) "nnumber:3" by blast+
3920    moreover AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xy›
3921    moreover AOT_assume ‹[F]x›
3922    ultimately AOT_have ‹[F]y›
3923      using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] by blast
3924  } note 1 = this
3925  AOT_have 0: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0n› by (metis "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3" Number.ψ)
3926  AOT_show ‹[F]n›
3927    apply (rule "pre-ind"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β, THEN "→E", OF "pred-thm:2", OF "pred-1-1:4", unvarify z, OF "zero:2",
3928THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]; safe intro!: 0 "&I" GEN "→I" F0)
3929    using 1 by blast
3930qed

3998                       THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast

4009  AOT_hence ‹[ℕ]b› by (metis "&E"(1) "≡E"(2) "nnumber:3")

4047AOT_theorem "pred-func:1": ‹[𝒫]xy & [𝒫]xz → y = z›
4048proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
4049  AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xy›
4050  AOT_hence ‹∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4051    using "pred-thm:3"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
4052  then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4053    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4054  then AOT_obtain a where Oa: ‹O!a› and a_prop: ‹[F]a & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧a)›
4055    using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
4056  AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xz›
4057  AOT_hence ‹∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(z,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4058    using "pred-thm:3"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
4059  then AOT_obtain G where ‹∃u ([G]u & Numbers(z,G) & Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧u))›
4060    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4061  then AOT_obtain b where Ob: ‹O!b› and b_prop: ‹[G]b & Numbers(z,G) & Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧b)›
4062    using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
4063  AOT_have ‹[F]⇧-⇧a ≈⇩E  [G]⇧-⇧b›
4064    using "num-tran:2"[unvarify G H, OF "F-u[den]", OF "F-u[den]", THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF
4065          a_prop[THEN "&E"(2)], OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]].
4066  AOT_hence ‹F ≈⇩E G›
4067    using "P'-eq"[unconstrain u, THEN "→E", OF Oa, unconstrain v, THEN "→E", OF Ob, THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "&I"]
4068          a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)] b_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)] by blast
4069  AOT_thus ‹y = z›
4070    using "pre-Hume"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2), OF "&I", OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)], OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]]
4071    by blast
4072qed

4362    proof (rule bij_betw_byWitness[where f'=b2])
4363      {

4383          using v_prop unfolding v_def

4385        then obtain v where v_def: ‹v = (THE v . [w⇩0 ⊨ [Π']«ωκ v»] ∧ [w⇩0 ⊨ [R]«ωκ a»«ωκ v»])› by blast

4405        by auto

4840AOT_theorem "modal-lemma": ‹◇∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v)›
4841proof(safe intro!: "→I" Ordinary.GEN)
4842  AOT_modally_strict {
4843    fix u
4844    AOT_assume act_Gu: ‹❙𝒜[G]u›
4845    AOT_have ‹∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v›
4846    proof(rule "→I")
4847      AOT_assume ‹∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v)›
4848      AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v› using "Ordinary.∀E" by fast
4849      AOT_thus ‹u ≠⇩E v› using act_Gu "→E" by blast
4850    qed
4851  } note 0 = this
4852  AOT_have θ: ‹□(∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v)› if ‹□❙𝒜[G]u› for u
4853  proof -
4854    AOT_have ‹□❙𝒜[G]u → □(∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v)›
4855      apply (rule RM) using 0 "&E" "→I" by blast
4856    thus ?thesis using that "→E" by blast
4857  qed
4858  fix u
4859  AOT_assume 1: ‹◇∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v)›
4860  AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜[G]u›
4861  AOT_hence ‹□❙𝒜[G]u›
4862    by (metis "Act-Basic:6" "≡E"(1))
4863  AOT_hence ‹□(∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v)› using Ordinary.ψ θ by blast
4864  AOT_hence ‹◇u ≠⇩E v› using 1 "K◇"[THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] by blast
4865  AOT_thus ‹u ≠⇩E v› by (metis "id-nec4:2" "≡E"(1)) 
4866qed

4868AOT_theorem "th-succ": ‹∀n∃!m [𝒫]nm›
4869proof(safe intro!: Number.GEN "→I" "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
4870  fix n
4871  AOT_have ‹NaturalCardinal(n)›
4872    by (metis "nat-card" Number.ψ "vdash-properties:10")
4873  AOT_hence ‹∃G(n = #G)›
4874    by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" card)
4875  then AOT_obtain G where n_num_G: ‹n = #G› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4876  AOT_hence ‹∃n (n = #G)› by (rule "Number.∃I")
4877  AOT_hence ‹◇∃y ([E!]y & ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
4878    using "modal-axiom"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"] by blast
4879  AOT_hence ‹∃y ◇([E!]y & ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
4880    using "BF◇"[THEN "→E"] by auto
4881  then AOT_obtain y where ‹◇([E!]y & ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4882  AOT_hence ‹◇E!y› and 2: ‹◇∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y)›
4883    using "KBasic2:3" "&E" "→E" by blast+
4884  AOT_hence Oy: ‹O!y›
4885    by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" intro: AOT_ordinary[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(2)])
4886  AOT_have 0: ‹∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y)› using 2 "modal-lemma"[unconstrain v, THEN "→E", OF Oy, THEN "→E"] by simp
4887  AOT_have 1: ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
4888  AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹Numbers(b, [λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y])›
4889    using "num:1"[unvarify G, OF 1] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4890  AOT_have Pnb: ‹[𝒫]nb›
4891  proof(safe intro!: "pred-thm:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]»›] 1 "∃I"(2)[where β=y] "&I" Oy b_prop)
4892    AOT_show ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]y›
4893      by (auto intro!:  "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "∨I"(2) "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Oy])
4894  next
4895    AOT_have equinum: ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]⇧-⇧y ≈⇩E [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]›
4896    proof(rule "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify F G, THEN "→E"]; ("cqt:2[lambda]" | rule "F-u[den]"[unvarify F]; "cqt:2[lambda]")?)
4897      AOT_show ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]⇧-⇧y ≡⇩E [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]›
4898      proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "F-u[den]"[unvarify F] Ordinary.GEN "→I"; "cqt:2[lambda]"?)
4899        fix u
4900        AOT_have ‹[[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ [(=⇩E)]xy]⇧-⇧y]u ≡ ([λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]u) & u ≠⇩E y›
4901          apply (rule "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[where τ⇩1τ⇩n=‹(_,_)›], simplified]; "cqt:2[lambda]"?)
4902          by (rule "beta-C-cor:2"[THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
4903        also AOT_have ‹… ≡  (❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y) & u ≠⇩E y›
4904          apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ [(=⇩E)]xy]u› ‹❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y›)
4905           apply (rule "beta-C-cor:2"[THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
4906          using "oth-class-taut:3:a" by blast
4907        also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜[G]u›
4908        proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
4909          AOT_assume ‹(❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y) & u ≠⇩E y›
4910          AOT_thus ‹❙𝒜[G]u› by (metis "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "∨E"(3) "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E")
4911        next
4912          AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜[G]u›
4913          AOT_hence ‹u ≠⇩E y› and ‹❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y›
4914            using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", OF Ordinary.ψ, THEN "→E"] "∨I" by blast+
4915          AOT_thus ‹(❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y) & u ≠⇩E y› using "&I" by simp
4916        qed
4917        also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]u›
4918          by (rule "beta-C-cor:2"[THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2), symmetric]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
4919        finally AOT_show ‹[[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ [(=⇩E)]xy]⇧-⇧y]u ≡ [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]u›.
4920      qed
4921    qed
4922    AOT_have 2: ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
4923    AOT_show ‹Numbers(n,[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]⇧-⇧y)›
4924      using "num-tran:1"[unvarify G H, OF 2, OF "F-u[den]"[unvarify F, OF 1],
4925                       THEN "→E", OF equinum, THEN "≡E"(2),
4926                       OF "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(2), OF n_num_G]].
4927  qed
4928  AOT_show ‹∃α ([ℕ]α & [𝒫]nα & ∀β ([ℕ]β & [𝒫]nβ → β = α))›
4929  proof(safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=b] "&I" Pnb "→I" GEN)
4930    AOT_show ‹[ℕ]b› using "suc-num:1"[THEN "→E", OF Pnb].
4931  next
4932    fix y
4933    AOT_assume 0: ‹[ℕ]y & [𝒫]ny›
4934    AOT_show ‹y = b›
4935      apply (rule "pred-func:1"[THEN "→E"])
4936      using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] Pnb "&I" by blast
4937  qed
4938qed

4959AOT_theorem "suc-fact": ‹n = m → n❙' = m❙'›
4960proof (rule "→I")
4961  AOT_assume 0: ‹n = m›
4962  AOT_show ‹n❙' = m❙'›
4963    apply (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF 0])
4964    by (rule "=I"(1)[OF "def-suc[den2]"])
4965qed

4967AOT_theorem "ind-gnd": ‹m = 0 ∨ ∃n(m = n❙')›
4968proof -
4969  AOT_have ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0m›
4970    using Number.ψ "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3" by blast
4971  AOT_hence ‹[[𝒫]⇧*]0m ∨ 0 =⇩𝒫 m›
4972    using "assume1:5"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
4973  moreover {
4974    AOT_assume ‹[[𝒫]⇧*]0m›
4975    AOT_hence ‹∃z ([[𝒫]⇧+]0z & [𝒫]zm)›
4976      using "w-ances-her:7"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β x, OF "zero:2", OF "pred-thm:2", THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", THEN "→E"]
4977      by blast
4978    then AOT_obtain z where θ: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0z› and ξ: ‹[𝒫]zm› using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4979    AOT_have Nz: ‹[ℕ]z› using θ "≡E"(2) "nnumber:3" by blast
4980    moreover AOT_have ‹m = z❙'›
4981    proof (rule "def-suc"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)];
4982           safe intro!: "def-suc[den1]"[unconstrain n, THEN "→E", OF Nz] "nec-hintikka-scheme"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "&I"
4983                        GEN "→I" "Act-Basic:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
4984      AOT_show ‹❙𝒜[ℕ]m› using Number.ψ
4985        by (meson "mod-col-num:1" "nec-imp-act" "vdash-properties:10")
4986    next
4987      AOT_show ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]zm› using ξ
4988        by (meson "nec-imp-act" "pred-1-1:1" "vdash-properties:6")
4989    next
4990      fix y
4991      AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜([ℕ]y & [𝒫]zy)›
4992      AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[ℕ]y› and ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]zy›
4993        using "Act-Basic:2" "&E" "≡E"(1) by blast+
4994      AOT_hence 0: ‹[𝒫]zy›
4995        by (metis RN "≡E"(1) "pred-1-1:1" "sc-eq-fur:2" "vdash-properties:10")
4996      AOT_thus ‹y = m›
4997        using "pred-func:1"[THEN "→E", OF "&I"] ξ by metis
4998    qed
4999    ultimately AOT_have ‹[ℕ]z & m = z❙'› by (rule "&I")
5000    AOT_hence ‹∃n m = n❙'› by (rule "∃I")
5001    hence ?thesis by (rule "∨I")
5002  }
5003  moreover {
5004    AOT_assume ‹0 =⇩𝒫 m›
5005    (* TODO: PLM: the proof takes a verbose route here *)
5006    AOT_hence ‹0 = m›
5007      using "id-R-thm:3"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β x, OF "zero:2", OF "pred-thm:2", THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", THEN "→E"]
5008      by auto
5009    hence ?thesis using id_sym "∨I" by blast
5010  }
5011  ultimately show ?thesis
5012    by (metis "∨E"(2) "raa-cor:1")
5013qed

5015AOT_theorem "suc-thm": ‹[𝒫]n n❙'›
5016proof -
5017  AOT_obtain x where m_is_n: ‹x = n❙'›
5018    using "free-thms:1"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF "def-suc[den2]"]
5019    using "∃E" by metis
5020  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([ℕ]n❙' & [𝒫]n n❙')›
5021    apply (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF suc_eq_desc[symmetric]])
5022    apply (rule "actual-desc:4"[THEN "→E"])
5023    by (simp add:  "def-suc[den1]")
5024  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[ℕ]n❙'› and ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]n n❙'›
5025    using "Act-Basic:2" "≡E"(1) "&E" by blast+
5026  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]nx›
5027    using m_is_n[symmetric] "rule=E" by fast+
5028  AOT_hence ‹[𝒫]nx›
5029    by (metis RN "≡E"(1) "pred-1-1:1" "sc-eq-fur:2" "vdash-properties:10")
5030  thus ?thesis
5031    using m_is_n "rule=E" by fast
5032qed

5034AOT_define Numeral1 :: ‹κ⇩s› ("1")
5035  "numerals:1": ‹1 =⇩d⇩f 0❙'›
5036
5037AOT_theorem AX:
5038  assumes 0: ‹∀F (∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[G]))›
5039  assumes G_prop: ‹¬(x[G] ≡ y[G])›
5040  shows ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5041proof -
5042  {
5043    AOT_assume ‹¬∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5044    AOT_hence 0: ‹∀F ¬([F]x & ¬[F]y)› by (metis "cqt-further:4" "vdash-properties:10")
5045    AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5046    proof (rule GEN; rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
5047      fix F
5048      AOT_assume ‹[F]x›
5049      moreover AOT_have ‹¬([F]x & ¬[F]y)› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)] by blast
5050      ultimately AOT_show ‹[F]y› by (metis "&I" "raa-cor:1") 
5051    next
5052      fix F
5053      AOT_assume ‹[F]y›
5054      AOT_hence ‹¬[λx ¬[F]x]y› by (metis "¬¬I" "β→C"(2))
5055      moreover AOT_have ‹¬([λx ¬[F]x]x & ¬[λx ¬[F]x]y)›
5056        apply (rule 0[THEN "∀E"(1)]) by "cqt:2[lambda]"
5057      ultimately AOT_have 1: ‹¬[λx ¬[F]x]x› by (metis "&I" "raa-cor:3")
5058      {
5059        AOT_assume ‹¬[F]x›
5060        AOT_hence ‹[λx ¬[F]x]x›
5061          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
5062        AOT_hence ‹p & ¬p› for p using 1 by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5063      }
5064      AOT_thus ‹[F]x› by (metis "raa-cor:1")
5065    qed
5066    AOT_hence ‹□∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)› using "ind-nec"[THEN "→E"] by blast
5067    AOT_hence ‹∀F □([F]x ≡ [F]y)› by (metis "CBF" "vdash-properties:10")
5068  } note indistI = this
5069  {
5070    AOT_assume G_prop: ‹x[G] & ¬y[G]›
5071    AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x›
5072      using "&E"(1) "∃I"(2) "→E" "encoders-are-abstract" by blast
5073
5074    {
5075      AOT_assume Ay: ‹A!y›
5076      {
5077        fix F
5078        {
5079          AOT_assume ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u)›
5080          AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ x[G]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)] "≡E" "→E" by meson
5081          AOT_hence ‹x[F]› using G_prop "&E" "≡E" by blast
5082        }
5083        AOT_hence ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → x[F]› by (rule "→I")
5084      }
5085      AOT_hence xprop: ‹∀F(∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → x[F])› by (rule GEN)
5086      {
5087        fix F
5088        {
5089          AOT_assume ‹∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u)›
5090          AOT_hence ‹□∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u)› by (metis "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]" "vdash-properties:10")
5091          AOT_hence ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u)› using "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"] by blast
5092          AOT_hence ‹x[F]› using xprop[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
5093        }
5094        AOT_hence ‹∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) → x[F]› by (rule "→I")
5095      }
5096      AOT_hence xprop: ‹∀F(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) → x[F])› by (rule GEN)
5097      moreover AOT_have yprop: ‹¬∀F(∀u□([F]u ≡ [G]u) → y[F])›
5098      proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
5099        AOT_assume A: ‹∀F(∀u□([F]u ≡ [G]u) → y[F])›
5100        moreover AOT_have ‹∀u□([G]u ≡ [G]u)›
5101          by (simp add: RN "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor" "vdash-properties:9")
5102        ultimately AOT_have ‹y[G]› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
5103        AOT_thus ‹p & ¬p› for p using G_prop "&E" by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5104      qed
5105      AOT_have ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5106      proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
5107        AOT_assume ‹¬∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5108        AOT_hence indist: ‹∀F □([F]x ≡ [F]y)› using indistI by blast
5109        AOT_have ‹∀F(∀u□([F]u ≡ [G]u) → y[F])›
5110          using indistinguishable_ord_enc_all[axiom_inst, THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "&I", OF "&I", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst], OF Ax, OF Ay, OF indist, THEN "≡E"(1), OF xprop].
5111        AOT_thus ‹∀F(∀u□([F]u ≡ [G]u) → y[F]) & ¬∀F(∀u□([F]u ≡ [G]u) → y[F])› using yprop "&I" by blast
5112      qed
5113    }
5114    moreover {
5115      AOT_assume notAy: ‹¬A!y›
5116      AOT_have ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5117        apply (rule "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«A!»›])
5118        using Ax notAy "&I" apply blast
5119        by (simp add: "oa-exist:2")
5120    }
5121    ultimately AOT_have ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›  by (metis "raa-cor:1")
5122  }
5123  moreover {
5124    AOT_assume G_prop: ‹¬x[G] & y[G]›
5125    AOT_hence Ay: ‹A!y›
5126      by (meson "&E"(2) "encoders-are-abstract" "existential:2[const_var]" "vdash-properties:10")
5127    AOT_hence notOy: ‹¬O!y›
5128      using "≡E"(1) "oa-contingent:3" by blast
5129    {
5130      AOT_assume Ax: ‹A!x›
5131      {
5132        fix F
5133        {
5134          AOT_assume ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u)›
5135          AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ x[G]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)] "≡E" "→E" by meson
5136          AOT_hence ‹¬x[F]› using G_prop "&E" "≡E" by blast
5137        }
5138        AOT_hence ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → ¬x[F]› by (rule "→I")
5139      }
5140      AOT_hence x_prop: ‹∀F(∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → ¬x[F])› by (rule GEN)
5141      AOT_have x_prop: ‹¬∃F(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & x[F])› 
5142      proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
5143        AOT_assume ‹∃F(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & x[F])›
5144        then AOT_obtain F where F_prop: ‹∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & x[F]› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5145        AOT_have ‹□([F]u ≡ [G]u)› for u using F_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"].
5146        AOT_hence ‹([F]u ≡ [G]u)› for u using "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"] by blast
5147        AOT_hence ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u)› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
5148        AOT_hence ‹¬x[F]› using x_prop[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
5149        AOT_thus ‹p & ¬p› for p using F_prop[THEN "&E"(2)] by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5150      qed
5151      AOT_have y_prop: ‹∃F(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & y[F])›
5152      proof (rule "raa-cor:1")
5153        AOT_assume ‹¬∃F (∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & y[F])›
5154        AOT_hence 0: ‹∀F ¬(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & y[F])› using "cqt-further:4"[THEN "→E"] by blast
5155        {
5156          fix F
5157          {
5158            AOT_assume ‹∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u)›
5159            AOT_hence ‹¬y[F]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)] using "&I" "raa-cor:1" by meson
5160          }
5161          AOT_hence ‹(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) → ¬y[F])› by (rule "→I")
5162        }
5163        AOT_hence A: ‹∀F(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) → ¬y[F])› by (rule GEN)
5164        moreover AOT_have ‹∀u □([G]u ≡ [G]u)›
5165          by (simp add: RN "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor" "vdash-properties:9")
5166        ultimately AOT_have ‹¬y[G]› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
5167        AOT_thus ‹p & ¬p› for p using G_prop "&E" by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5168      qed
5169  
5170      AOT_have ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5171      proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
5172        AOT_assume ‹¬∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5173        AOT_hence indist: ‹∀F □([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5174          using indistI by blast
5175        AOT_thus ‹∃F(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & x[F]) & ¬∃F(∀u □([F]u ≡ [G]u) & x[F])›
5176          using indistinguishable_ord_enc_ex[axiom_inst, THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "&I", OF "&I", OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst],
5177OF Ax, OF Ay, OF indist, THEN "≡E"(2), OF y_prop] x_prop "&I" by blast
5178      qed
5179    }
5180    moreover {
5181      AOT_assume notAx: ‹¬A!x›
5182      AOT_hence Ox: ‹O!x›
5183        using "∨E"(3) "oa-exist:3" by blast
5184      AOT_have ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5185        apply (rule "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«O!»›])
5186        using Ox notOy "&I" apply blast
5187        by (simp add: "oa-exist:1")
5188    }
5189    ultimately AOT_have ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)› by (metis "raa-cor:1")
5190  }
5191  ultimately AOT_show ‹∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5192    using G_prop by (metis "&I" "deduction-theorem" "≡I" "raa-cor:1")
5193qed
