5195notepad
5196begin
5197  AOT_modally_strict {
5198    AOT_have A: ‹∀F (∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[G])) & ¬(x[G] ≡ y[G]) → ∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)› for x y G
5199      using AX "→I" "&E" by blast
5200
5201    {
5202      fix x y G
5203      {
5204        AOT_assume 0: ‹∀F (∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[G]))›
5205        AOT_assume ‹∃H (∀u([H]u ≡ [G]u) & ¬(x[H] ≡ y[H]))›
5206        then AOT_obtain H where H_prop: ‹∀u([H]u ≡ [G]u) & ¬(x[H] ≡ y[H])› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5207        {
5208          fix F
5209          {
5210            AOT_assume ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [H]u)›
5211            AOT_hence 1: ‹[F]u ≡ [H]u› for u using "Ordinary.∀E" by fast
5212            moreover AOT_hence 2: ‹[F]u ≡ [G]u› for u using H_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"]
5213              by (metis "≡E"(5))
5214            ultimately AOT_have 3: ‹[H]u ≡ [G]u› for u by (metis "≡E"(6))
5215            AOT_hence ‹∀u([H]u ≡ [G]u)› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
5216            AOT_hence ‹x[H] ≡ x[G]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
5217            moreover {
5218              AOT_have ‹[F]u ≡ [G]u› for u using 1 2 3
5219                by meson
5220              AOT_hence ‹∀u ([F]u ≡ [G]u)› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
5221              AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ x[G]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
5222            }
5223            ultimately AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ x[H]› by (metis "deduction-theorem" "≡I" "≡E"(1) "≡E"(2))
5224          }
5225          AOT_hence ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [H]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[H])› by (rule "→I")
5226        }
5227        AOT_hence asm1: ‹∀F(∀u([F]u ≡ [H]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[H]))› by (rule GEN)
5228        AOT_have ‹∃F ([F]x & ¬[F]y)› using AX[OF asm1, OF H_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]] by blast
5229      } note t = this
5230
5231      AOT_hence 0: ‹¬∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y) → ¬(∀F (∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[G])) & ¬(x[G] ≡ y[G]))›
5232        for x y G using "contraposition:1[1]"
5233        using A by presburger
5234      {
5235        fix x y G
5236        AOT_assume ‹¬∃F([F]x & ¬[F]y)›
5237        AOT_hence ‹¬(∀F (∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[G])) & ¬(x[G] ≡ y[G]))› using 0[THEN "→E"] by blast
5238        AOT_hence ‹¬∀F (∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[G])) ∨ (x[G] ≡ y[G])›
5239          using "&I" "∨I"(1) "∨I"(2) "reductio-aa:1" by meson
5240        AOT_hence ‹∀F (∀u([F]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[F] ≡ x[G])) → (x[G] ≡ y[G])›
5241          using "¬¬I" "∨E"(2) "deduction-theorem" by meson
5242      }
5243    }
5244  }
5245end
5246
5247AOT_theorem denotes_all': ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]↓›
5248proof -
5249  AOT_modally_strict {
5250    fix x y
5251    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5252    AOT_hence nec_indist: ‹□∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)› 
5253      using "ind-nec" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
5254    AOT_hence indist_nec: ‹∀F □([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5255      using "CBF" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
5256    AOT_assume 0: ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])›
5257    AOT_have ‹x[F]›
5258      by (safe intro!: 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] GEN "→I" RN "≡I")
5259    AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])›
5260    proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
5261      AOT_assume ‹¬∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])›
5262      AOT_hence ‹∃G ¬(∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])› using "cqt-further:2" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
5263      then AOT_obtain G where G_prop: ‹¬(∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5264      AOT_hence 1: ‹∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) & ¬y[G]› by (metis "≡E"(1) "oth-class-taut:1:b")
5265      AOT_have xG: ‹x[G]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] 1[THEN "&E"(1)] by blast
5266      AOT_hence ‹x[G] & ¬y[G]› using 1[THEN "&E"(2)] "&I" by blast
5267      AOT_hence B: ‹¬(x[G] ≡ y[G])›
5268        using "&E"(2) "≡E"(1) "reductio-aa:1" xG by blast
5269      {
5270        fix H
5271        {
5272          AOT_assume 3: ‹∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u)›
5273          {
5274            fix u
5275            AOT_have ‹[H]u ≡ [G]u› using 3[THEN "Ordinary.∀E"] by blast
5276            also AOT_have ‹[G]u ≡ [F]u› using 1[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"] by blast
5277            finally AOT_have ‹[H]u ≡ [F]u›.
5278          }
5279          AOT_hence ‹∀u ([H]u ≡ [F]u)› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
5280          AOT_hence ‹x[H]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)] "→E" by blast
5281          AOT_hence ‹x[H] ≡ x[G]› using xG "≡I" "→I" by blast
5282        }
5283        AOT_hence ‹∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[H] ≡ x[G])› by (rule "→I")
5284      }
5285      AOT_hence A: ‹∀H(∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[H] ≡ x[G]))› by (rule GEN)
5286      then AOT_obtain F where F_prop: ‹[F]x & ¬[F]y› using AX[OF A, OF B] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5287      moreover AOT_have ‹[F]y› using indist[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(1), OF F_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]].
5288      AOT_thus ‹p & ¬p› for p using F_prop[THEN "&E"(2)] by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5289    qed
5290  } note 0 = this
5291  AOT_modally_strict {
5292    fix x y
5293    AOT_assume ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5294    moreover AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]y ≡ [F]x)›
5295      by (metis calculation "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(2))
5296    ultimately AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G]) ≡ ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])›
5297      using 0 "≡I" "→I" by auto
5298  } note 1 = this
5299  AOT_show ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]↓›
5300    by (safe intro!: RN GEN "→I" 1 "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
5301qed
5302
5303AOT_theorem denotes_ex': ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])]↓›
5304proof -
5305  AOT_modally_strict {
5306    fix x y
5307    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5308    AOT_hence nec_indist: ‹□∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)› 
5309      using "ind-nec" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
5310    AOT_hence indist_nec: ‹∀F □([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5311      using "CBF" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
5312    AOT_assume 0: ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])›
5313    AOT_have ‹¬x[F]›
5314      by (safe intro!: 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] GEN "→I" RN "≡I")
5315    AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬y[G])›
5316    proof(rule "raa-cor:1")
5317      AOT_assume ‹¬∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬y[G])›
5318      AOT_hence ‹∃G ¬(∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬y[G])› using "cqt-further:2" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
5319      then AOT_obtain G where G_prop: ‹¬(∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬y[G])› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5320      AOT_hence 1: ‹∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) & ¬¬y[G]› by (metis "≡E"(1) "oth-class-taut:1:b")
5321      AOT_hence yG: ‹y[G]›
5322        using G_prop "deduction-theorem" "raa-cor:3" by blast
5323      moreover AOT_hence 12: ‹¬x[G]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] 1[THEN "&E"(1)] by blast
5324      ultimately AOT_have ‹¬x[G] & y[G]› using "&I" by blast
5325      AOT_hence B: ‹¬(x[G] ≡ y[G])› by (metis "12" "≡E"(3) "raa-cor:3" yG)
5326      {
5327        fix H
5328        {
5329          AOT_assume 3: ‹∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u)›
5330          {
5331            fix u
5332            AOT_have ‹[H]u ≡ [G]u› using 3[THEN "Ordinary.∀E"] by blast
5333            also AOT_have ‹[G]u ≡ [F]u› using 1[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"] by blast
5334            finally AOT_have ‹[H]u ≡ [F]u›.
5335          }
5336          AOT_hence ‹∀u ([H]u ≡ [F]u)› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
5337          AOT_hence ‹¬x[H]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)] "→E" by blast
5338          AOT_hence ‹x[H] ≡ x[G]› using 12 "≡I" "→I" by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5339        }
5340        AOT_hence ‹∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[H] ≡ x[G])› by (rule "→I")
5341      }
5342      AOT_hence A: ‹∀H(∀u ([H]u ≡ [G]u) → (x[H] ≡ x[G]))› by (rule GEN)
5343      then AOT_obtain F where F_prop: ‹[F]x & ¬[F]y› using AX[OF A, OF B] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5344      moreover AOT_have ‹[F]y› using indist[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(1), OF F_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]].
5345      AOT_thus ‹p & ¬p› for p using F_prop[THEN "&E"(2)] by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5346    qed
5347  } note 0 = this
5348  AOT_modally_strict {
5349    fix x y
5350    AOT_assume ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5351    moreover AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]y ≡ [F]x)›
5352      by (metis calculation "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(2))
5353    ultimately AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G]) ≡ ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬y[G])›
5354      using 0 "≡I" "→I" by auto
5355  } note 1 = this
5356  AOT_show ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])]↓›
5357    by (safe intro!: RN GEN "→I" 1 "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
5358qed
5359
5360AOT_theorem denotes_equiv: ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F]))]↓›
5361proof -
5362  AOT_modally_strict {
5363    fix x y
5364    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5365    {
5366      AOT_assume xF: ‹x[F]›
5367      AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F])) → ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (y[G] ≡ y[F]))›
5368      proof(safe intro!: "→I")
5369        AOT_assume 0: ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F]))›
5370        AOT_have ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]↓›
5371          using denotes_all' by blast
5372        AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]x ≡ [λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]y›
5373          using indist[THEN "∀E"(1)] by blast
5374        moreover AOT_have ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]x›
5375        proof (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) denotes_all' "cqt:2" GEN "→I")
5376          fix G
5377          AOT_assume ‹∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u)›
5378          AOT_hence ‹x[G] ≡ x[F]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
5379          AOT_thus ‹x[G]› using xF by (metis "≡E"(2))
5380        qed
5381        ultimately AOT_have ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]y› using "≡E" by blast
5382        AOT_hence 1: ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])›
5383          by (rule "β→C"(1))
5384        moreover AOT_have ‹∀u ([F]u ≡ [F]u)›
5385          by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor" "vdash-properties:9")
5386        ultimately AOT_have yF: ‹y[F]› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
5387        AOT_show ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (y[G] ≡ y[F]))›
5388        proof (safe intro!: GEN "→I")
5389          fix G
5390          AOT_assume ‹∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u)›
5391          AOT_hence ‹y[G]› using 1[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=G], THEN "→E"] by blast
5392          AOT_thus ‹y[G] ≡ y[F]› using yF "≡I" "→I" by blast
5393        qed
5394      qed
5395    } 
5396    moreover {
5397      AOT_assume notxF: ‹¬x[F]›
5398      AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F])) → ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (y[G] ≡ y[F]))›
5399      proof(safe intro!: "→I")
5400        AOT_assume 0: ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F]))›
5401        AOT_have ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])]↓›
5402          using denotes_ex' by blast
5403        AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])]x ≡ [λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])]y›
5404          using indist[THEN "∀E"(1)] by blast
5405        moreover AOT_have ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])]x›
5406        proof (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) denotes_ex' "cqt:2" GEN "→I")
5407          fix G
5408          AOT_assume ‹∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u)›
5409          AOT_hence ‹x[G] ≡ x[F]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
5410          AOT_thus ‹¬x[G]› using notxF by (metis "≡E"(4))
5411        qed
5412        ultimately AOT_have ‹[λx ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬x[G])]y› using "≡E" by blast
5413        AOT_hence 1: ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → ¬y[G])›
5414          by (rule "β→C"(1))
5415        moreover AOT_have ‹∀u ([F]u ≡ [F]u)›
5416          by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor" "vdash-properties:9")
5417        ultimately AOT_have notyF: ‹¬y[F]› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
5418        AOT_show ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (y[G] ≡ y[F]))›
5419        proof (safe intro!: GEN "→I")
5420          fix G
5421          AOT_assume ‹∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u)›
5422          AOT_hence ‹¬y[G]› using 1[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=G], THEN "→E"] by blast
5423          AOT_thus ‹y[G] ≡ y[F]› using notyF "≡I" "→I" by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5424        qed
5425      qed
5426    }
5427    ultimately AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F])) → ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (y[G] ≡ y[F]))›
5428      by (metis "raa-cor:1")
5429  } note 1 = this
5430  AOT_modally_strict {
5431    fix x y
5432    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5433    AOT_hence indist': ‹∀F ([F]y ≡ [F]x)›
5434      by (metis "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(1))
5435    AOT_have ‹∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F])) ≡ ∀G (∀u ([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (y[G] ≡ y[F]))›
5436      using 1[OF indist] 1[OF indist'] "≡I" by blast
5437  } note 1 = this
5438  show ?thesis
5439    apply (safe intro!: RN GEN "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "→I")
5440    using 1 by blast
5441qed
5442
5443AOT_theorem Comprehension:
5444  assumes ‹∀F∀G □(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))›
5445  shows ‹[λx ∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})]↓›
5446proof -
5447  AOT_modally_strict {
5448    fix x y
5449    AOT_assume assms: ‹∀F∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))›
5450    AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5451    thm denotes_equiv
5452    AOT_have ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) → ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F})›
5453    proof(safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
5454      fix F
5455      AOT_assume 0: ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})›
5456      {
5457        fix G
5458        {
5459          AOT_assume ‹∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u)›
5460          AOT_hence ‹φ{F} ≡ φ{G}› using assms[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
5461          moreover AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ φ{F}›  using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)].
5462          moreover AOT_have ‹x[G] ≡ φ{G}›  using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)].
5463          ultimately AOT_have ‹x[G] ≡ x[F]› by (metis "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a")
5464        }
5465        AOT_hence ‹∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F])› using "→I" by blast
5466      }
5467      AOT_hence 1: ‹∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F]))› by (rule GEN)
5468      AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F]))]x›
5469        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) denotes_equiv intro: "cqt:2")
5470      AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (x[G] ≡ x[F]))]y›
5471        using indist[THEN "∀E"(1), OF denotes_equiv, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
5472      AOT_hence 2: ‹∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (y[G] ≡ y[F]))› by (rule "β→C"(1))
5473      AOT_show ‹y[F] ≡ φ{F}›
5474      proof (safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
5475        AOT_assume yF: ‹y[F]›
5476        {
5477          fix G
5478          {
5479            AOT_assume ‹∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u)›
5480            AOT_hence ‹y[G]› using 2[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2)] yF by blast
5481          }
5482          AOT_hence ‹∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G]› by (rule "→I")
5483        }
5484        AOT_hence ‹∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])› by (rule GEN)
5485        AOT_hence ‹[λy ∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])]y›
5486          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) denotes_all' intro: "cqt:2")
5487        AOT_hence ‹[λy ∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])]x›
5488          using indist[THEN "∀E"(1), OF denotes_all', THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
5489        AOT_hence ‹∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])› by (rule "β→C"(1))
5490        moreover AOT_have ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [F]u)›
5491          by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor" "vdash-properties:9")
5492        ultimately AOT_have ‹x[F]› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
5493        AOT_thus ‹φ{F}› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
5494      next
5495        AOT_assume ‹φ{F}›
5496        AOT_hence xF: ‹x[F]› using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
5497        {
5498          fix G
5499          {
5500            AOT_assume ‹∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u)›
5501            AOT_hence ‹x[G]› using 1[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2)] xF by blast
5502          }
5503          AOT_hence ‹∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G]› by (rule "→I")
5504        }
5505        AOT_hence ‹∀G(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])› by (rule GEN)
5506        AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀G(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]x›
5507          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) denotes_all' intro: "cqt:2")
5508        AOT_hence ‹[λx ∀G(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → x[G])]y›
5509          using indist[THEN "∀E"(1), OF denotes_all', THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
5510        AOT_hence ‹∀G(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → y[G])› by (rule "β→C"(1))
5511        moreover AOT_have ‹∀u([F]u ≡ [F]u)›
5512          by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor" "vdash-properties:9")
5513        ultimately AOT_show ‹y[F]› using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
5514      qed
5515    qed
5516  } note 1 = this
5517  AOT_modally_strict {
5518    AOT_assume 0: ‹∀F∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))›
5519    {
5520      fix x y
5521      {
5522        AOT_assume indist: ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y)›
5523        AOT_hence indist': ‹∀F ([F]y ≡ [F]x)›
5524          by (metis "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(1))
5525        AOT_have ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) ≡ ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F})›
5526          using 1[OF 0, OF indist] 1[OF 0, OF indist'] "≡I" by blast
5527      }
5528      AOT_hence ‹∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y) → (∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) ≡ ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F}))› using "→I" by blast
5529    }
5530    AOT_hence ‹∀y(∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y) → (∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) ≡ ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F})))› for x
5531      by (rule GEN)
5532    AOT_hence ‹∀x∀y(∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y) → (∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) ≡ ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F})))›
5533      by (rule GEN)
5534  } note 1 = this
5535  AOT_hence ‹❙⊢⇩□ ∀F∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G})) → ∀x∀y(∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y) → (∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) ≡ ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F})))›
5536    by (rule "→I")
5537  AOT_hence ‹□∀F∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G})) → □∀x∀y(∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y) → (∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) ≡ ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F})))›
5538    by (rule RM)
5539  moreover {
5540    AOT_have ‹∀F∀G □(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))› using assms by blast
5541    AOT_hence ‹□(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))› for F G using "∀E"(2) by blast
5542    AOT_hence ‹∀G □(∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))› for F by (rule GEN)
5543    AOT_hence ‹□∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))› for F
5544      using "BF" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
5545    AOT_hence ‹∀F □∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))› by (rule GEN)
5546    AOT_hence ‹□∀F∀G (∀u([G]u ≡ [F]u) → (φ{F} ≡ φ{G}))›
5547      using "BF" "vdash-properties:10" by fast
5548  }
5549  ultimately AOT_have 1: ‹□∀x∀y(∀F ([F]x ≡ [F]y) → (∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}) ≡ ∀F (y[F] ≡ φ{F})))›
5550    using "→E" by blast
5551  show ?thesis
5552    apply (safe intro!: "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
5553    using 1 by blast
5554qed

5558(* Note: we forgo restricted variables for natural cardinals. *)
5559AOT_define Finite :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹Finite'(_')›)
5560  "inf-card:1": ‹Finite(x) ≡⇩d⇩f NaturalCardinal(x) & [ℕ]x›
5561AOT_define Infinite :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹Infinite'(_')›)
5562  "inf-card:2": ‹Infinite(x) ≡⇩d⇩f NaturalCardinal(x) & ¬Finite(x)›
5563
5564AOT_theorem "inf-card-exist:1": ‹NaturalCardinal(#O!)›
5565  by (safe intro!: card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«O!»›] "=I" "num-def:2"[unvarify G] "oa-exist:1")
5566
5567AOT_theorem "inf-card-exist:2": ‹Infinite(#O!)›
5568proof (safe intro!: "inf-card:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "inf-card-exist:1")
5569  AOT_show ‹¬Finite(#O!)›
5570  proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
5571    AOT_assume ‹Finite(#O!)›
5572    AOT_hence 0: ‹[ℕ]#O!›
5573      using "inf-card:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E"(2) by blast
5574    AOT_have ‹Numbers(#O!, [λz ❙𝒜O!z])›
5575      using "eq-num:3"[unvarify G, OF "oa-exist:1"].
5576    AOT_hence ‹#O! = #O!›
5577      using "eq-num:2"[unvarify x G, THEN "≡E"(1), OF "oa-exist:1", OF "num-def:2"[unvarify G], OF "oa-exist:1"]
5578      by blast
5579    AOT_hence ‹[ℕ]#O! & #O! = #O!› using 0 "&I" by blast
5580    AOT_hence ‹∃x ([ℕ]x & x = #O!)›
5581      using "num-def:2"[unvarify G, OF "oa-exist:1"] "∃I"(1) by fast
5582    AOT_hence ‹◇∃y ([E!]y & ∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
5583      using "modal-axiom"[axiom_inst, unvarify G, THEN "→E", OF "oa-exist:1"] by blast
5584    AOT_hence ‹∃y ◇([E!]y & ∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
5585      using "BF◇"[THEN "→E"] by blast
5586    then AOT_obtain b where ‹◇([E!]b & ∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E b))›
5587      using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5588    AOT_hence ‹◇[E!]b› and 2: ‹◇∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E b)›
5589      using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast+
5590    AOT_hence ‹[λx ◇[E!]x]b›
5591      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
5592    moreover AOT_have ‹O! = [λx ◇[E!]x]›
5593      by (rule "rule-id-df:1[zero]"[OF "oa:1"]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
5594    ultimately AOT_have b_ord: ‹O!b›
5595      using "rule=E" id_sym by fast
5596    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜O!b›
5597      by (meson "≡E"(1) "oa-facts:7")
5598    moreover AOT_have 2: ‹∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E b)›
5599      using "modal-lemma"[unvarify G, unconstrain v, OF "oa-exist:1", THEN "→E", OF b_ord, THEN "→E", OF 2].
5600    ultimately AOT_have ‹b ≠⇩E b›
5601      using "Ordinary.∀E"[OF 2, unconstrain α, THEN "→E", OF b_ord, THEN "→E"] by blast
5602    AOT_hence ‹¬(b =⇩E b)› by (metis "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E")
5603    moreover AOT_have ‹b =⇩E b›
5604      using "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF b_ord].
5605    ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5606  qed
5607qed
